INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('11', '17', '袁家界', '14671011725183.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 115px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">“美国科幻大片《阿凡达》取景地、哈利路亚悬浮山原型所在地”</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/755-3.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 720px; height: 465px;\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">峰林奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>位于武陵源核心景区中心位置，平均海拔1074米，为一方山台地，背依岩峰山峦，面临幽谷群峰，自东向西延伸，是武陵源核心景区的风景集中地。袁家界名称相传来源于后唐时期，黄巢起义失败后，有一名姓“袁”的义军将士，为躲避朝廷追捕，便来到了这远离人世的深山野岭隐居生活，并以自己的姓氏为这里命名，起名“袁家界”。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界袁家界峰林\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271413305495.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界袁家界峰林\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;峰林 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摄影者：张建国</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">袁家界面积约1200公顷，平均海拔1074米，它东邻<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>、远眺<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1070.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">鹞子寨</a>；南望<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1067.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄石寨</a>，连接天波府；西通<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>；北距索溪峪。它位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界国家森林公园</a>北部，是镶嵌在武陵源核心景区的一颗明珠。袁家界位于杉刀沟北麓，是以石英岩为主构成的一座巨大而较平缓的山岳。袁家界是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>公园又一处风景集中地。自金鞭溪紫草潭左入杉刀沟可上袁家界；顺袁家界台地边沿，绕荒径小道亦可下至金鞭溪千里相会处；亦可从袁家界去天子山、杨家寨。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"张家界袁家界阿凡达\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271400220155.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界袁家界阿凡达\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">袁家界景区虽然在地域上隶属于中国第一个国家森林公园——张家界国家森林公园，但从地理位置上来说，却被众星捧月般地位居张家界武陵源风景名胜区的核心，与世界上最美丽的峡谷金鞭溪一衣带水，东接索溪峪，南眺鹞子寨，西望黄石寨，北靠天子山，总面积约1200公顷，平均海拔1074米。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>站在袁家界景区的观景台上，三千奇峰尽收眼底，雄险秀野，神态各异。峡谷深处，千百根石峰石柱奇伟突立。峻峭之石，如英武将帅；嵯峨之峰，似勇猛壮士。有声有色，若静若动，形象逼真，呼之欲出。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">美景风光</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"哈利路亚山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271400533245.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"哈利路亚山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摄影者：宋志光</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>景色之美有“<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>后花园”之称，后来因美国科幻大片《阿凡达》在此取景而名声大噪。来到袁家界，一步一景美妙绝伦，原来，电影中的潘多拉星球真的存在。悬浮山的原型“南天一柱”现被更名为 “哈利路亚山”，“潘多拉太远，张家界很近”的广告词更是脍炙人口，传播甚广。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"空中田园\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271406422244.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"空中田园\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;摄影者：陈明明</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">景区内的代表性景点有：百龙天梯，世界上最高、载重量最大、运行速度最快的户外观光电梯；天下第一桥，桥面宽两米，厚四米，跨度为二十多米，高度为三百多米，是世界是迄今为止所发现落差最高的天然石桥。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">推荐理由</h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">最具特色的百龙天梯，垂直高差335米，运行高度326米，由154米山体内坚井和172米贴山钢结构井架等组成，采用三台双层全暴露观光电梯并列分体运行，每台次载客50人次，运行速度3米/秒，三台同时运行每小时往返量达4000人次。百龙天梯的修建实现“山上游，山下住”的目标，提供了交通保障，将<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>天下第一桥、迷魂台、天悬白练以及乌龙寨、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>等绝世美景从幕后推向了前台，并将<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>、袁家界、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>等精品旅游线路连为一体，解决了多年困扰景区的交通瓶颈问题。</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁50米）就可搭乘去往森林公园、武陵源的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">武陵源吴家峪门票站进入：乘景区环保车至百龙天梯下站，乘电梯上山。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">森林公园门票站进入：步行至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>千里相会景点处，从乱窜坡游道步行上山。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">或者从<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>索道、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>索道上山后，乘景区环保车前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">武陵源核心景区游览路线可简要形容为山下游览路线、山上游览路线；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>属于山上游览线，可作为游览的起点，1日游推荐线路为：武陵源区-吴家峪门票站-景区环保车-百龙天梯上山-袁家界-景区环保车-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>-景区环保车-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>-天子山索道下山-景区环保车-吴家峪门票站-武陵源区，整线游览时间至少需7小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">袁家界为半环形游览线，迷魂台停车场进入景区-沿游道步行-天下第一桥停车场处景区，游览时间约1.5小时。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '2');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('66', '52', '八大公山', '14672547275429.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">简介</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"八大公山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/272047340897.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"八大公山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1130.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">八大公山</a>自然保护区总面积2万公顷，分为天平山、杉木界、斗篷山三大林区，主峰斗篷山海拔1898.4米，为武陵山脉南麓之巅。气候属北亚热带山地湿润季风气候，夏秋季短，春冬季长，最冷月平均气温0.1℃，最热月平均气温22.8℃，相对湿度90%以上。区内群山起伏，山脉纵横交错，599座山峰星罗棋布，奇峰突起，溪流、瀑布众多。独特的地理环境，孕育和保存了亚热带最完整、面积最大原生型常绿阔叶林。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界八大公山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/272047553808.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界八大公山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">户外攻略</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">【资源种类】原生性森林、瀑布、山峦</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">【户外项目】徒步山地穿越、溯溪、岩降、瀑降、水上抱石、定向越野、野营等</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">【海拔范围】346m至2003m</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">【线路难度】5星</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">【线路强度】4星</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">【线路风景】4星</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">【装备要求】速干衣裤、冲锋衣、防寒衣、登山包、登山鞋、登山杖、水袋、手套、头巾、野炊用具、露营装备、头盔、药品等</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">【周边资源】<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1099.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙故居</a>、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1103.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">廖汉生故居</a>、桑鹤土司结盟遗址、澧水源头七眼泉等。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">【交通指引】</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0\">1.进入：桑植汽车西站至芭茅溪乡（20元），然后租车进入辽竹湾村（穿越的起点）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0\">2.回程：下山后再沙园联系芭茅溪车主接至芭茅溪，原路返回桑植县。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">行程</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">DAY1</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">桑植县-芭茅溪-四门岩林场</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">[备注]桑植县至芭茅溪乡后中餐，推荐参观：圆梦饭庄（价格20-30元/人，联系电话：13974426576）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">中餐后租车往辽竹湾，在辽竹湾村部下车后沿小路步行10km左右至四门岩林场，宿营四门岩林场场部。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">DAY2</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">四门岩林场-长坪-大顶坪</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">[备注]</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">从四门岩林场出发，翻山至长坪峡谷入口，沿长坪沟溯溪而上，长坪午休，午休后顺干谷河床一路向上提升面，直达大顶坪宿营。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">DAY3</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">大顶坪-瞭望塔-小庄坪（天平山接待站）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">DAY4</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">小庄坪-连三台-毛垭半坡</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">[备注]沿山腰猎户小道环山至青龙湾，青龙湾对面有一小溪沟，顺沟而下可见三棵枯树，再往下见干枯河床，顺河床而下至漆水塔休息。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">顺峡谷而下行至毛垭半坡农户家宿营。全程无手机信号，需9小时。晚上可<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1201.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">住宿</a>当地农家，体验土家族的日常生活。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">DAY5</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">毛垭半坡-黄连台（李家河）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">[备注]</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">早餐后从毛垭半坡至毛垭村，有小卖部补结，从毛垭村小路下山至黄连台村长宿营，全天行程需7小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">黄连台村村长杨志山15074408816</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 书记刘伟华13407443072</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">DAY6</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">黄连台-小溪口-天梯人家-七湾-芭茅溪</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">[备注]</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">至黄连台村部，沿溪边土公路往下到达小溪口，公路可达芭茅溪镇，公路旁小溪进山约40分钟山路到达天梯人家，此处可观60m瀑布。天梯人家徒步七湾下山到达天平山公路，可联系包车来接至芭茅溪，车费30元/车（司机张师傅13707446937）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img alt=\"张家界八大公山地图\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/272049474905.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界八大公山地图\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">安全提示</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">【安全提示】该线路需要扁带、对讲机、急救药品等公共装备方可成行，切勿孤身或私下结伴前往，需联系当地户外俱乐部提供专业向导和保护。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">此行程路途较长，而且进入谷底，手机信号不好，也有可能没有；又出于隐雷区，雨天建议慎重出行。谷中暂时没有小商品出售，进入景区要带足食物和饮水保持体力，可以带些高能量的食物，如巧克力、饼干、肉类等；景区中有许多飞禽走兽，请远离并保护它们，切勿伤害它们；山中雨雾笼罩，有时豁然开朗，横穿石壁，自然温服比较低，风力也会大些，请务必注意保暖，适当带些衣服，防止温度突变，引起身体不适。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">特别提醒：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1130.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">八大公山</a>毒蛇（五步蛇）出没，要防止被毒蛇咬伤。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">遇险求助电话：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">八大公山乡政府0744-6730001</span></p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br/></span></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('10', '17', '张家界森林公园', '14671010559715.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 115px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">“扩大的盆景.缩小的仙境”，人生不到张家界，百岁岂能称老翁？</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/755-5.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 720px; height: 465px;\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">地质公园</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">“中国首批世界自然遗产、世界首批地质公园、国家首批5A级旅游景区”【武陵源核心景区】为是来<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>游人的必玩景区，因独特的“张家界石英砂岩峰林地貌”而闻名于世，由<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界国家森林公园</a>、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>风景区、索溪峪风景区（部分）共同组成，门票为通票制，下辖7个分景区，分别为【<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>】、【天子山】、【<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>】、【<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>】、【<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>】、【<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1067.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄石寨</a>】、【<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1070.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">鹞子寨</a>】，自然风光各不相同。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;奇山异水张家界，举世闻名，是湖南核心旅游景点，还有世界溶洞之冠的<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1079.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄龙洞</a>，神秘幽深。有峰林之称的天子山，不到黄石寨，枉到张家界，还有世界上最美丽的峡谷金鞭溪。</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">美景风光</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">上亿年前的地壳运动，大自然的鬼斧神工，造就了<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>不可复制的神奇和美丽。于是，无数游过张家界的人赞叹：人生不到张家界，访尽千山也枉然，人生不到张家界 百岁何能称老翁？张家界是“扩大的盆景.缩小的仙境”，随着四季的气象不同变幻莫测，是大自然鬼斧神功美的让人心动。张家界集桂林之秀、黄山之奇、华山之险、泰山之雄于一体，藏赂、桥、洞、湖、瀑于一身，有“扩大的盆景、缩小的仙山”之美称。</span></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界杨家界峰墙\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/261039042596.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界杨家界峰墙\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>峰墙</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界国家森林公园</a>位于湖南省西北部张家界市境内，是1982年由国务院委托国家计委批准成立的中国第一个国家森林公园，1992年12月因奇特的石英砂岩大峰林被联合国列入《世界自然遗产名录》，2004年2月被列入世界地质公园。公园自然风光以峰称奇、以谷显幽、以林见秀。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界天子山卧龙岭\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/261040580484.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天子山卧龙岭\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>卧龙岭 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：刘君</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">公园属于中亚热带气候区，高山峡谷，茂密的森林，使公园形成了独特的森林小气候——冬暖夏凉，年平均气温12.8℃，夏天平均最高气温16.8℃，冬天平均最低气温9.6℃，公园空气清新，含负氧离子高，身临其中，人体感觉特别舒适，是休闲避暑的理想之地。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界袁家界\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/261043149132.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界袁家界\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">绝美自然景观。张家界地处于云贵高原隆起区与洞庭湖沉降区之间，既受隆起的影响，又受沉降的牵制 ,加上地表水切割强烈和岩溶地貌极其发育，形成了当今这种高低悬殊、奇峰林立、万石峥嵘、溪谷纵横的自然奇观。是户外爱好者的旅行天堂。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界十里画廊小火车\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/271601423959.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界十里画廊小火车\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">独特的人文景观。土家族、白族、苗族、侗族和瑶族等少数民族占整个张家界市的96%。具有浓烈的民族风情，是人文摄影爱好者的必去之地。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界金鞭溪\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/261044519598.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界金鞭溪\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者： 汤东涛</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">及其优良的气候条件。四季分明，冬 长夏短。每年3月起，气温日渐升高，春意盎然，兽鸟活跃，山峦田野，充满着生机与活力，同时此时降雨较多，可看到云海。到了6月下旬，武陵源开始进入夏季，直至9月上旬。武陵源夏季的平均气温在22至26摄氏度之间，最高时也不过32摄氏度左右。此时，许多地区酷热难熬，而这里却一派清凉，是避暑消夏的理想去处之一。冬季景区山顶与市区截然不同，张家界虽然地处南方，但还是有雪景的出现！是冬季摄影的好去处！</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界黄石寨\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/261046028952.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界黄石寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &