INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('12', '17', '十里画廊', '14671011992233.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 115px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">自然鬼斧神工，仙师山水画卷 人游山峡里，宛如画图中 以车代步、轻松观景、舒适悠闲</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/755-4.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 720px; height: 465px;\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">山水画卷</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>，位于武陵源核心景区中部，来回全长10里。峡谷两旁千峰耸立，林木葱笼，野花飘香；奇峰异石，千姿百态，像一幅巨大的山水画卷，并排悬挂在千韧绝壁之上，使秀美绝伦的自然奇观溶进仙师画工的水墨丹青之中；人行其间，三步一景，如在画中遨游，故有“十里画廊”之美誉。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界十里画廊\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271341425442.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界十里画廊\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">十里画廊是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界国家森林公园</a>景区内的旅游精华，在这条长达十余里的山谷两侧，有着丰富的自然景观，人行其间如在画中。沟旁黛峰屏列，山上的岩石形成了200来尊似人似物、似鸟似兽的石景造型，其中“孔雀开屏”、“采药老人”、“寿星迎宾”、“猛虎啸天”等最为著名。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">美景风光</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界十里画廊小火车\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271346472423.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界十里画廊小火车\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>是核心景区内，目前唯一可乘交通工具全程游览的景区，观光电车不仅是游客朋友以车代步、轻松观景的美妙体验载体，更是游览十里画廊最佳的观景方式，改变了游客欣赏风景的角度和视野，被誉为“<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>最美的流动风景线”。&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界十里画廊\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271342241657.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界十里画廊\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;星海采药 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摄影者：贾长江</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">推荐理由</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">有人说，<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>是在大自然有无穷灵感的时候，恣意描绘出的一幅神奇绝美的画卷！诗人黎盛鸣游毕赋诗:“奇峰争起闹长空,百态千姿造化功。秀谷清溪十里路,游人多少画廊中。”雕塑家钱绍武称其为“一条天然雕塑杰作的群像陈列长廊”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">十里画廊内可谓步步有景，处处如画。在这条长达十余里的山谷两侧，有着丰富的自然景观，人行其间如在画中。沟旁黛峰屏列，山上的岩石形成了200来尊似人似物、似鸟似兽的石景造型，沿途主要景点有寿星迎宾、采药老人、猛虎啸天、夫妻抱子、转阁楼、三姐妹等。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁50米）就可搭乘去往森林公园、武陵源的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">武陵源吴家峪门票站进入：乘景区环保车至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">森林公园门票站进入：步行至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>尽头水绕四门停车场，乘景区环保车至十里画廊。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">游览<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>，时间约1.5小时。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">武陵源核心景区游览路线可简要形容为山下游览路线、山上游览路线；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">十里画廊属于山下游览线，1日游推荐线路为：市区-森林公园门票站-徒步<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>-水绕四门-景区环保车-十里画廊-景区环保车-吴家峪门票站-武陵源区，整线游览时间至少需6小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">此外，穿过十里画廊，沿尽头卧龙岭游道，可徒步登上<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">门票：已含在武陵源核心景区门票内（票价248元/3天有效）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市武陵源区十里画廊风景区</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '4');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('13', '17', '黄石寨', '14671012585242.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 115px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">不上黄石寨，枉到张家界， 张家界最大的凌空观景台</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/756.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 720px; height: 465px;\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">凌空观景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">俗话说“不上<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1067.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄石寨</a>，枉到<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>”。黄石寨，位于张家界市的武陵源，是国家5条精品游览线之一。相传汉朝张良，看破红尘，辞官不做，隐居江湖。在云游这里时，被官兵围困。后来得师父黄石公的帮助脱险，因而把这里叫作黄石寨。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界黄石寨索道\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271323212601.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界黄石寨索道\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">美景风光</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1067.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄石寨</a>海拔1200米，占地面积250亩，为<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界森林公园</a>最大、 最集中的观景台，主要观景点有20余处，故有“不上黄石寨，枉到<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>”之说。有南北两条步行登寨游道，还有后山车道自老磨湾通通寨后卡门，系砂石路面；从南面登寨，沿途有天书宝匣、定海神针、南天门、南天一柱、摘星台、天桥遗墩、六奇阁等绝佳景点。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界黄石寨\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271323578413.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界黄石寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">游人这样评价黄石寨：五步称奇，七步叫绝；十步之外，目瞪口呆。黄石寨这里的每一座岩峰都是一件古老的艺术品，它们如剑、如针、如龙首、如老龟、如现代化都市的摩天大厦……曾有诗曰：“千峰竟秀，万木葱笼，琳琅满目，美不胜数。虽非大上，不似人间，借以喻此，不为过也。”</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界黄石寨雪景\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271324124611.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界黄石寨雪景\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁50米）就可搭乘去往森林公园的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">森林公园门票站进入：从老磨湾广场乘景区环保车至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1067.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄石寨</a>索道下站，乘缆车上山。或从登山游道步行上山（时间约1.5小时）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">武陵源核心景区游览路线可简要形容为山下游览路线、山上游览路线；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1067.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄石寨</a>归属于山下游览线，1日游推荐线路为：市区-森林公园门票站-老磨湾广场-黄石寨索道上山-黄石寨-黄石寨索道下山-徒步<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>-水绕四门-景区环保车-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>-景区环保车-吴家峪门票站-武陵源区，整线游览时间至少需7小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">如果选择步行上下山，时间增加约3小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">黄石寨山顶为环形游道，有小环线（1.5小时）、大环线（3小时）之分。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">相关信息</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">门票：已含在武陵源核心景区门票内（票价</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">248</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">元</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">/3</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">天有效）</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市武陵源区黄石寨风景区</span></p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br/></span></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('14', '17', '天子山', '14671012875839.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 115px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">扩大的盆景，缩小的仙境</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/755-1.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;padding: 0px;width: 720px;height: 465px\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">峰林奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天子山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271456235998.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天子山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摄影者：文绍军</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>位于武陵源核心景区东北面，海拔</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1200</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">多米，景区内石峰林立，沟壑纵横，被誉为“扩大的盆景，缩小的仙境”。相传，土家民族英雄“向王天子”，带领土家族人反对朝廷暴政。在此与前来围剿的官兵殊死搏斗，兵败后宁死不屈，跳下了神堂湾。人们为了</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">念这位土家族英雄，而取名“天子山”。即使后来清王朝采用各种压抑措施。强令取消“天子”二字。但土家族人民却一直称“天子山”。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天子山雪景\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271456524049.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天子山雪景\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摄影者：赵敏</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">因景区内峰林耸立如海，故被游人赞为“峰林之王”。那些遗世而独立的石峰，屹立在岁月的长河中，以至于每一座孤峰都拥有着生命，向您无言地倾诉着他们积攒下的无数故事。不会腾云的我们，只能在路可以相连的山壁上行走。而那些雄壮的山体，也许再过</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">十万载，又演变成了新的峰林。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天子山云海\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271259359819.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天子山云海\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：孙建华</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>还有“云雾、月夜、霞日、冬雪”四大奇观。天子山最多见的云雾奇观，景象万千，有云雾、云海、云涛、云瀑、云彩等。久雨初晴之后或霏霏细雨之中，先是朦胧大雾，继而形成白云，环绕飘浮。群峰在无边无际的云海中时隐时现，使人仿佛置身于蓬莱仙境之中。霞日，晴天的早晨，一轮红日在朵朵红云的衬托下，从奇山异峰中冉冉升起。千万座石塔，婷婷玉立，披上一层红霞，十分迷人。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天子山雪景\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271259482692.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天子山雪景\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;摄影者：孙建华</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">冬雪，入冬，天子山银装素裹，青松和峰顶被大雪覆盖。此时的天子山冰柱倒立，冰花四散，只有一些山鹿、野猪，才不为银白世界所征服。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁50米）就可搭乘去往武陵源的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">武陵源吴家峪门票站进入：乘景区环保车至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>索道下站，乘缆车上山，或从卧龙岭步行上山。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">或者从<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">杨家界</a>索道、百龙天梯上山后，乘景区环保车前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">武陵源核心景区游览路线可简要形容为山下游览路线、山上游览路线；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>属于山上游览线，可作为游览的起点，1日游推荐线路为：武陵源区-吴家峪门票站-景区环保车-天子山索道上山-天子山-景区环保车-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">杨家界</a>-景区环保车-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">袁家界</a>-百龙天梯下山-景区环保车-吴家峪门票站-武陵源区，整线游览时间至少需7小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">天子山常规游览多在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1101.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙公园</a>游览区（时间约2小时）。如果时间允许，体力充沛，可选择去茶盘塔游览区（时间约1.5小时）、老屋场游览区游览（时间约3小时）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">老屋场云海是最直接推荐的拍摄地，云雾缭绕，仙气逼人。从丁香榕路口至老屋场，尚有4公里余山路，可乘当地面包车、三轮车前往。若是选择徒步，要考虑此道是一路下坡，路上布满石子，晴天三尺土，雨天一身泥。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">门票：已含在武陵源核心景区门票内（票价248元/3天有效）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市武陵源区天子山风景区</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('15', '17', '鹞子寨', '14671013246054.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; display: block; width: 110px; height: 110px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 110px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center;\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">石寨遗址</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1070.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">鹞子寨</a>位于武陵源核心景区东南面，海拔1050米，相传明清和民国年间，这里还是当地百姓躲避兵匪的地方，现仍存有石寨遗址，据说鹞子都难以飞过，山形又如同一只展翅欲飞的鹞子，所以取名叫鹞子寨。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">鹞子寨距森林公园门票站仅200米，是武陵源核心景区内面积最大，线路最长，景点最多的游览区。以险、奇、雄、野而著称，是户外徒步的最佳之地，需要充沛的体力。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300920285598.jpg\" alt=\"张家界鹞子寨景区\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界鹞子寨景区\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">鹞子寨的入口是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界国家森林公园</a>大氧吧广场。往鹞子寨方向的游人都是性情中人，或只身前往，或三五成群。有的时候，群山之中，甚至只有你一个人。但是对于户外探险爱好者来说，这无疑是一个优势，远离拥挤的人潮、鼎沸的人声，近距离倾听自然的脉动。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">从入口到百应谷，是一段平路，分为梅花路、军乐路、脚印路三段，每一段都有自己独特的符号。军乐路上是一个个约一米长的琴键，或高或低，如音符般点缀在路旁。原生态的游道两旁，丛林茂密，树木擎天，即便是艳阳高照的夏日，也只有几处阳光细线般洒落。沿途的路标，在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>的所有景点里也是一个独创，它不仅标有景点名，还有海拔高程。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/>如果够幸运，你可以看到黄鼠狼、锦鸡等野生动物穿梭在丛林中。记者去的时候，正值初秋，有幸领略到了“万绿丛中一点红”的佳景。若是深秋，整个<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1070.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">鹞子寨</a>，一层红艳，一层深绿，层层叠叠，相间而生，那景色，岂一个“美”字了得？</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300921049786.jpg\" alt=\"张家界鹞子寨景区\" width=\"730\" height=\"449\" title=\"张家界鹞子寨景区\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">鹞子寨之“险”，让您领略无限风光在众峰，体验胆颤心惊、回味无穷的惊险经历，“凌空惊魂”等景点，将是您人生旅途难以忘怀的亮点。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">鹞子寨之“奇”，让您感叹造物主的生气和伟大，惟妙惟肖的“梭镖峰”，能上能下的“天桥”等景点，为您增添新的阅历和记载。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">鹞子寨之“雄”，让您饱尝一览众山小豪迈，“万笋争春”，“将军阅兵”等景点，带您体验万里江山尽收眼底的霸气。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">鹞子寨之“野”，让您远离城市的喧嚣，清泉石上流，山花四季香，猴戏鸟语蝉鸣， “花香溪”、“万花争妍”等景点，给您徒步的享乐，花草的芬香，天簌的声音。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300921402340.jpg\" alt=\"张家界鹞子寨景区\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界鹞子寨景区\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">从百应谷到寨顶，约莫20分钟。天晴的时候，寨顶偶尔可见老鹰掠过的身影，那就是鹞子。到了寨顶再顺着环寨游道绕一圈要30来分钟，沿途可以看到老鹰嘴、梭镖岩、指点江山、凌空惊魂等景点。每一处景点的石碑，都是由中国人民解放军将军们亲笔题写，其中“鹞子寨”三字就是上将张万年亲自题写。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁50米）就可搭乘去往森林公园的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">森林公园门票站进入：步行200米至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1070.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">鹞子寨</a>山门。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">游览<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1070.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">鹞子寨</a>，时间最少需4小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">因鹞子寨为独立的山峰，游览时间较长，1日游推荐线路为：市区-森林公园门票站-鹞子寨-骆驼峰-进入<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>-水绕四门-景区环保车-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>-景区环保车-吴家峪门票站-武陵源区，整线游览时间至少需8小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">门票：已含在武陵源核心景区门票内（票价248元/3天有效）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市武陵源区鹞子寨风景区</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('16', '17', '金鞭溪', '14671013557280.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 115px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center;\">世界上最美丽的峡谷之一，一片充满着童话般的世界</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/756-2.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 720px; height: 465px;\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">最美峡谷</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>&nbsp;是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>的黄金旅游区，全长5700米，溪水发源于土地垭，从张家界林场场部到水绕四门，蜿转曲折，幽静异常，随山而移，穿行在峰峦幽谷云间，迤逦延伸于鸟语花香之中。因溪水流经金鞭岩而得名。金鞭溪全长6.5公里，自西向东贯通森林公园，两岸奇峰屏列，风光如画，嬉戏的鸟兽、古奇的树木、悠然的游鱼、景色显得异常幽静。金鞭溪所经之地被誉为“世界上最美丽的峡谷”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界金鞭溪\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271237235165.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界金鞭溪\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：汤东涛</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">主要景致有醉罗汉、神鹰护鞭、金鞭岩、花果山、水帘洞、劈山救母、千里相会、楠木坪、水绕四门等。其中，金鞭岩拔地而起380多米，整块岩石为石英砂构成，在阳光的照耀下反射出熠熠金光，使得这根“石鞭”被冠以“金”的定语。金鞭岩身边一山峰状若护雏的老鹰，威风凛凛，日夜守护着“金鞭”，故而被称为神鹰，这片景得名“神鹰护鞭”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">一块巨大的岩石从当中裂开，取名为“沉香救母”。这缘于一个古老的传说：一个叫沉香的孩子，他的母亲因触犯天条被压在了山脚。小沉香为救母亲，苦练本领，最终用利斧劈开山峰，救出了母亲。“花果山”、“水廉洞”是美猴王孙悟空的天下，在《西游记》里早已为人们所熟悉。总之，这一段景色犹如世外桃源，不能不令人流连忘返。水绕四门为<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>与矿洞溪、龙尾溪汇合处，溪谷宽阔，御案峰奇秀迷人，万岁牌传说神秘。 &nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界金鞭溪\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271237578413.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界金鞭溪\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;摄影者：韦伟群</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">金鞭溪穿行在峰峦幽谷间，把<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>的山水发挥到了淋漓尽致，溪水明净，跌宕多姿，小鱼游弋其中。溪畔花草鲜美，鸟鸣莺啼，人沿清溪行，胜似画中游。不仅有“千年长旱不断流，万年连雨水碧青”这样的美誉；著名文学家沈从文先生赞誉它是“张家界的少女”，著名画家吴冠中先生曾赞美她是“一片充满着童话般的世界”。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界金鞭溪猕猴\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271238124777.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界金鞭溪猕猴\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;摄影者：宋志光</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">金鞭溪自然环境原生态，动植物种类多样，主要分布常绿和落叶阔叶林，而主要树种为楠木，更有国家一级保护植物，<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1140.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">珙桐</a>和水杉。金鞭溪沿溪遍布着一种形状怪异的花，它的形状特别像龙虾，故名<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1142.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">龙虾花</a>。龙虾花是一种珍贵的草本植物，大小不同，颜色各异，有红色、蓝色、黄色等。溪里有一种“<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1133.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">娃娃鱼</a>”，世界上现存最大的也是最珍贵的两栖动物，属国家二级保护动物。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁50米）就可搭乘去往森林公园的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">森林公园门票站进入：从老磨湾广场步行进入<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">游览<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>全程，时间最少需3小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">金鞭溪属于山下游览线，1日游推荐线路为：市区-森林公园门票站-徒步金鞭溪-水绕四门-景区环保车-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1066.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">十里画廊</a>-景区环保车-吴家峪门票站-武陵源区，整线游览时间至少需6小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">门票：已含在武陵源核心景区门票内（票价248元/4天有效）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市武陵源区金鞭溪风景区</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('17', '17', '杨家界', '14671014001012.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; display: block; width: 110px; height: 110px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 110px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center;\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">峰墙奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>景区东连<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>，北邻<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>，总面积34平方公里，除了峰墙奇观，还有石柱、古藤、飞瀑、五色花等自然美景和乌龙寨等人文风景。由于山势险峻，交通不畅，普通游客难以企及，多年来只在户外驴友中享有盛名，峰墙奇观多半处于雪藏状态。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">而2014年刚投入运行的“空中走廊”杨家界索道，向世人尽早揭开了杨家界的面纱，展示了杨家界峰墙的稀缺之美、原始之美、形体之美和文化之美，将过去的遥不可及将变得触手可及。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界杨家界峰墙\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271436127993.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界杨家界峰墙\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">10年（1998年至2008年）前的杨家界还是一个被游人遗忘的角落的话，10年（1998年至2008年）后的今天，她作为<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>与天子山的姐妹山，就已经走出闺阁，走出武陵源，已让很多来自五湖四海的朋友亲睹了她的芳容。杨家界风景区同张家界一样，一开始也是“养在深闺人未识”，可刚一露头角，便是“一举成名天下知”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">湘潭大学教授羊春秋老先生游览了杨家界后，盛赞道：“清秀、壮丽、险特、雄奇，使人为之倾倒，为之拍案惊奇。” 山西大学副教授周征松说：“杨家界新发现的又一个神奇世界。这里山势壮丽，奇峰林立，俊俏无比。”自从1991年3月12日《人民日报》海外版与同年3月23日《人民日报》国内版刊登武陵源新发现杨家界旅游风景区的消息以后，不久便有100多家报刊、电台与电视台报道，因此不久在北京、上海、广州与香港便掀起了“杨家界热”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">环球国际社《今日中国》杂志社摄影部主任王新民、华艺出版社梁希毅、《工人日报》记者何碧宝、湖南省人民政府对台办主任王习年以及美过国几位朋友，到杨家界以后，一进山就被这里的秀丽风光迷住了，一连几天住在山洞里欣赏自然风光。他们异口同声赞扬：“杨家界自然风光美不胜收，叫人留连忘返！”<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界杨家界索道\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271436263584.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界杨家界索道\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">杨家界风景，同张家界一样，主要是原始风光自然美。它张家界、天子山、索溪峪比较，除地质地貌与一部分山峰基本相同以外，又有其独特之处，不似张家界，一部分景观又胜似张家界。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">美景风光</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界杨家界乌龙山寨\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271438060127.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界杨家界乌龙山寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">游玩<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>，可谓野趣横生。这里的乌龙寨曾是土匪盘踞的山寨，建于断崖深谷旁，地势险要。进入乌龙寨有“过三关”之说，第一道关“一步难行”，那是一段陡峭的石级，攀登时往往要手足并用。第二关“谁能不低头”，这里的路需要钻洞绕石，小心低头弯腰才能通过。第三关“一线天”，又叫“瘦身关”，需要侧着身子，才能慢慢地从这两块巨石间穿过。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">著名景点天波府是近距离观赏“峰墙奇观”绝佳之地，那相对平行而立的十余道石墙，皆高矮参差不齐，气势恢宏，巍峨壮观，宛如造物主铸就的“自然长城”。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界杨家界天波府\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271439107620.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界杨家界天波府\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">除了这几处特别有灵气的景点以外，杨家界山水也是很美的。这里供有景点 杨家界风景区110处，既有造型独特的山峰与危崖，又有流翠滚玉一般溪流与飞瀑：既有以前窝藏土匪的“歪嘴岩”，又有奇绝难攀的“鬼愁寨”：还有“马蹄岩”、“猿愁攀”、“天波府”、“姐妹湾”等许多奇景，真是写不尽，看不完。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">这里还要特别提到“宗保峰”、“六郎峰”、“佘太君”、“杨家界”，这些名字是什么意思？原来这杨家界的一些山名，都是杨家将子孙后代为纪念杨家将而取的地名，一千多年来，一直沿袭未改，所以来杨家界游览，不仅可以饱览这里的原始风光，同时还可以替杨家寻祖问根，继承并发扬爱国忠良的遗风。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁50米）就可搭乘去往森林公园、武陵源的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">森林公园门票站进入：老磨湾广场步行至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1067.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">黄石寨</a>索道下站，从索道站左手旁公路上山步行至龙凤庵，搭乘景区环保车至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>索道下站，可乘缆车或步行上山（约2小时） 。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">武陵源吴家峪门票站进入：乘景区环保车至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>索道下站或百龙天梯下站，乘缆车或电梯上山。或者从卧龙岭或乱窜坡步行上山。上山后，乘景区环保车前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, tahoma, arial, Verdana, sans-serif, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, 宋体; font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">武陵源核心景区游览路线可简要形容为山下游览路线、山上游览路线；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">杨家界</a>属于山上游览线，可作为游览的起点，1日游推荐线路为：市区-森林公园门票站-老磨湾广场-龙凤庵-杨家界索道上山-杨家界-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>-<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天子山</a>-天子山索道下山-吴家峪门票站-武陵源区，整线游览时间至少需7小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">杨家界常规游览区域在乌龙寨、天波府一线（时间约2小时）。如果体力充沛，可选择去一步登天、空中走廊等（时间约2小时）。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('18', '17', '龙凤梯田', '14671014455046.png', '<p>									</p><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">田园之韵</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201507/081639268890.jpg\" alt=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摄影者：代天胜</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1324.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">龙凤梯田</a>始建于春秋战国时期，形成至今已有上千年的历史，是龙凤村历代先民的劳动结晶，是稻作文化的历史遗存，是人类物质文化发展的见证者，是一块躲在深山里的旅游胜地。这里山地连绵，层峦叠嶂，阡陌纵横，气势磅礴，从高处远望，万亩梯田，层层相间，梯田线条变幻无穷，有的舒缓流畅，有的蜿蜒曲折，梯田随季节变化，呈万千气象。眺望那山、那云海、那梯田、那山寨一应俱全，与日月共辉。不仅是观赏和拍摄日出、日落、云海、梯田最佳的地方，还是具有海中之寨的绝美仙境。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201507/081640235475.jpg\" alt=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：代天胜</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">龙凤梯田位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市西北部，属永定区罗水乡管辖，与天泉山国家森林公园背靠着背紧紧相连。上亿万年前，在云贵高原的强烈造山运动作用下与武陵山脉相撞击而形成龙凤梯田原型、龙凤山脉。其梯田规模宏大、历史悠久，相传为明初土家族农民起义军领袖覃垕率领数万大军开垦而来，距今已七百多年了，堪舆广西龙胜的龙脊梯田媲美。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">最美田园</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201507/081641164684.jpg\" alt=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">去龙凤村观梯田美景的最佳时节应是春耕与秋收两季，站在天泉山的抱儿岩垭口可以俯瞰龙凤村全貌，为最佳观景之处。龙凤村至今还算是个比较原始的村落，修了一条不足4米宽的毛坯土公路，若要留宿山上欣赏日出日落美景，可以住在老百姓的农家乐，也可以自带帐篷露营，不过，山上可供扎帐露营的地方还真不少，大大小小的自然草坪有好几十处，水源洁净、充沛又方便，任由你挑选。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201507/081641345023.jpg\" alt=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>龙凤山下的沟谷中就是永定区特色文化乡镇--罗水乡政府所在地，每年的古历&quot;六月六&quot;（覃垕晒皮）都会在乡政府边上一个名叫南梁寨的村子里，举办一次有中国戏剧“活化石”之称的土家族茅古斯舞风情表演，以纪念农民起义军领袖覃垕，游客可以随时参加六月六<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">活动</a>。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">一、从<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>出发：张家界市内<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">—</span>三家馆乡<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">—</span>温塘镇<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">—</span>天泉山公园<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">—</span>龙凤村<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">—</span>罗水乡（或桥头乡）<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">--</span>教子垭镇<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">—</span>尹家溪镇<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">—</span>市内。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span>二、从桑植出发：桑植县城、老火电厂后面出发，经过老牙槽、永定青安平五家湾、天泉山国家森林公园直达关门岩<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">&quot;</span><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1324.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">龙凤梯田</a><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">&quot;&nbsp;</span>观景台。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">建议自驾游，全程来回<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">130</span>公里，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2</span>个小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '11');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('19', '18', '天门山国家森林公园', '14671024229082.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">门洞奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>国家森林公园有着深厚的文化底蕴，有着&quot;武陵之魂&quot;之美誉，更有湘西第一神山的美誉，它兼峰、石、泉、溪、云、林于一体，集雄、奇、秀、险、幽于一身，被誉为空中原始花园。我们乘坐天门山索道，前往游览天门山：观天门洞、99道弯公路奇观（通天大道）、鬼谷栈道、鬼谷兵盘、云梦仙顶、天门山寺、灵泉院、木石之恋等著名景点。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/281722211893.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天门山洞\" align=\"\" alt=\"张家界天门山洞\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">因“世界海拔最高的天然穿山溶洞”【天门洞】而得名，惊险刺激的天门山特技飞行表演就曾多次在这里举行。可搭乘“世界上最长的高山观光索道”【天门索道】，从市中心直达山顶，让人得享“一步达天界”的惊奇乐趣。天门山顶自然环境原生态，被人称为【空中花园】。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"天门山索道\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281725103720.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"天门山索道\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图片天门山提供/摄影者李纲</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"天门山鬼谷栈道\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281721343358.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"天门山鬼谷栈道\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;图片<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>提供/摄影者：李东群</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">待到雨前雨后，悬于鬼谷洞上侧，立于峭壁之上的【鬼谷栈道】，雾气盘绕，山间云海翻腾，抬腿似生雾，迈步如踏云，仿佛人间天界。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天门山盘山公路\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271211213777.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天门山盘山公路\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">除自然美景之外，全长10.77公里的天门山“盘山公路”，也同样世界知名。盘山公路平均每米造价为1万人民币，号称中国公路最高，海拔高度有200米一路提升至1300米，期间180度发夹弯多达99处，符合“天有九重，云有九霄”之意。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天门山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271212015647.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天门山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天门山寺\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271219354974.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天门山寺\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">天门山寺是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>天门山的新传奇，2009年6月8日，佛舍利子安家<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1090.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门寺</a>，此枚释迦牟尼佛舍利不仅是湖南省首枚，也是中国目前仅有的五枚之一。寺庙建筑古雅清幽，奇巧恢弘，视野开阔，极目东南，众山皆小，确有一山独尊的气概，是湘西的佛教中心。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">每年的3月19日、6月19日、9月19日被张家界人定位观音娘娘的生辰，每年的这个时候张家界人就会一起上天门山的天门山寺祈祷，有信仰的您如果也真好是这天来到天门就一定要和大家一起祈祷哟。 &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在市区可乘<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">5</span>、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">6</span>、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">10</span>路等公交至市区<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>索道下站，乘缆车至天门山国家森林公园。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">游览景区至少需<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">5</span>小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">在市区可乘<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">5</span>、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">6</span>、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">10</span>路等公交至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>索道下站，乘缆车至索道上站，游览山顶。山顶为环形游览线，分东、西两线。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">游完山顶，乘缆车至索道中站，转乘景区环保车至天门洞游览。随后，乘车返回索道中站，乘缆车下山。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">门票：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">258</span>元</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市区官黎坪天门山索道下站（纬地酒店对面）</p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('20', '18', '宝峰湖', '14671024538543.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 115px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">高峡起平湖，峰林上的空中圣湖</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/751-3.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;padding: 0px;width: 720px;height: 465px\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">空中圣湖</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1072.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">宝峰湖</a>主要景点由宝峰湖和鹰窝寨两大块组成。其中宝峰湖、奇峰飞瀑、鹰窝寨、一线天被称为武陵源“四绝”。是武陵源风景名胜中的精品景点。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>它是一座罕见的高峡平湖，四面青山，一泓碧水，风光旖旎，是山水风景杰作。宝峰湖水深72米，长2.5米公里，以其秀丽的湖光水色与幽野的洞天情趣成为武陵源水景风光的代表之作，电视剧《西游记》中花果山水帘洞外景就拍摄于“奇峰飞瀑”。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界宝峰湖\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271148577155.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界宝峰湖\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">湖中有两座叠翠小岛，近岸奇峰屹立，峰回水转。泛舟漫游，只见一湖绿水半湖倒影，充满诗情画意。“云梯万丈上天台，高峡平湖一鉴开，王母瑶池金扶，浣沙仙女下凡来”游宝峰湖，你就会欣赏到这样的诗情画意。群峰拥抱的宝峰湖，长约2.,5公里，湖犹如一面宝镜，四面青山，一泓碧水，荡桨温游，格外惬意。坐在船上，环顾四周，千山耸翠，俯视水中，倒影慢移，碧水照相馆得群峰绿，人面桃花水映红。真是静极了，美极了！</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界宝峰寺\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271149155264.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界宝峰寺\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 神秘的宝峰寺</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">韩剧《<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a>》拍摄的湖水就是宝峰湖。在湖中漫游，还可以见到湖心岛上的一些佳景，如“仙女照镜”、“高峡平湖”、“金蟾含月”也各有特色。鹰窝寨为宝峰公园一景，进公园后西向登山数百石级，头顶的石峰裂缝如线，入口处有古城门雉堞，尽处有宝峰古寺，香火旺盛。崖上石径直上峰顶，相传旧社会有匪首如鹰盘踞山顶小寨。一线天是宝峰公园的一大绝景。峡谷长200余米，高100余米，平均宽度不足两米，中有小溪，溪畔石级盘旋而上，清幽无比，曲奥无穷。该游览线还有一系列景点，著名的鹰窝寨位于宝峰湖西南一绝壁之上。早年是著名的土匪寨子，电视剧《乌龙山剿匪记》就拍摄于此。</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">地质与地貌：武陵源景区内的巨厚的石英砂岩，产状平缓，使岩层不能沿层面薄弱部位滑塌，覆盖在志留系柔性的页岩之上。重力作用，使得刚性的石英砂岩垂直节理发育，在水流强烈的侵蚀作用下，岩层不但解体、崩塌，流水搬运，残留在原地的便形成雄、奇、险、秀、幽、旷等千奇百怪的峰林，是武陵源风景区的主体。流水侵蚀地貌，在这里一个突出的表现是由于地壳上升，溪流向下切割作用加大，来不及将河流拓宽，而使河谷形成隘谷、峡谷。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"5A景区宝峰湖\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271152543374.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"5A景区宝峰湖\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">河的谷底极窜成线形，两壁陡峻。咱们<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1072.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">宝峰湖</a>就是这种地貌。当你泛舟湖上，湖水那纤尘不染、婀娜多姿，悠然自得的特点使你感觉超然于世，进入忘我的境界。两岸陡峻秀丽的景色，又使你留恋人生，感叹造物主的神奇。身边猛然响起阿哥阿妹动情的对唱，又会把你带回湖上，让你感受到这人世间最纯朴的真爱。这就是为什么众多的年青人，也有不少中老年人，到了<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>，非到宝峰湖来不可，真谛，也许就在这里。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界宝峰湖\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271151065368.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"449\" title=\"张家界宝峰湖\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">宝峰湖是世界自然遗产、世界地质公园、首批国家5A级旅游区组成部分。湖中有两座叠翠小岛，群山拥抱，奇峰屹立，一湖绿水碧波，充满诗情画意。泛舟湖上环顾四周，千山耸翠，水中倒影慢移，此一既静且美之绝景，着实他处难寻。在湖中漫游，还可以偶然间邂逅俊俏淳朴的土家阿哥、阿妹的原生态山野民歌对唱，让人远离尘世喧嚣，回归宁静自然。</span></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在武陵源区，乘<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2</span>路公交车前往。</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">游览景区，最少需2小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1072.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">宝峰湖</a>为环形游览线，进入景区后，一般沿右手方向开始进行游览。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('21', '18', '茅岩河漂流', '14671024877332.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">漂流奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>是澧水上游50多公里长的一段河。茅岩河是一幅多彩多姿、生动活泼的水国画，是一帧竞奇斗艳、婀娜多娇的青山图。清代光绪《永定县乡士志》载曰：“澧自苦竹河入境，重滩叠濑，其著者八十有奇，浪头河大多奇险”。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>澧水在湖南湘、资、沅、澧四大水系中，排名老幺，而性情十分刚烈，凶猛异常。吞噬生命，扫荡原野，曾使多少人家破人亡。因而人们一度谈澧色变，称它为“魔水”、“鬼河”。特别是当它发疯时，人们几乎用尽了一切诅咒的字眼咒骂它，渐渐地忘却了它的美丽。直到茅岩河漂流的兴起，澧水美丽的面孔才重新走进人们的视野。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界茅岩河\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271517310271.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界茅岩河\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;摄影者：代天胜</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">从湖北发源的澧水，在连绵不断的山峡里喧泄奔腾，到永定区温塘镇后，在较为开阔的盆谷里，绕着一架青山盘缠歇息。造物主就是这么奇妙，澧水长途奔泄的余威还未荡平，河两岸的群山突然收缩，山哥山弟齐心协力拼死挤压澧水，不甘被挤扁的澧水，在山峡里，同巍巍大山展开了搏斗，于是造就了茅岩河之奇观。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">河水更为凶悍强劲，昂头撤蹄，湍湍东去。一滩连一滩，一浪挽一浪。百里河流百里滩，百里流水百里浪。<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>水无情地撞击着河中根基深厚的礁石，尽管撞击得头破血流，断肠裂肺，粉身碎骨，依然无怨无悔，从不停歇地演绎着生命的壮观。被撕碎的生命化成点点银珠抛上天空，继而又落回永不消逝的躯体上，织就了一幅生生不息的王母娘娘洒降甘露图。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img alt=\"张家界茅岩河漂流\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271521234845.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界茅岩河漂流\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">而被河水冲撞了千百年仍然傲然屹立的礁石，撕破了河水刚刚要向人展示玉脂般的肌肤，又被汹涌而至的河水淹没，再次击起满天银花。前进与阻挡相搏发生的巨大轰鸣，在河谷里一次又一次的回响，在群山中一次又一次地震荡。若乘坐皮筏或小舟在河上漂流，一种无以言状的享受游走在每根神经。人时而被软若无骨的河水抛上浪尖，时而又被它牵扯着跌入峰谷。会不由自主地发出享受大自然赋予的刺激的无险惊叫。尖叫声与浪涛声汇成了一支欢乐的乐章。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/271518342764.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界茅岩河漂流\" align=\"\" alt=\"张家界茅岩河漂流\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">茅岩河漂流这是继<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界国家森林公园</a>开放以后开辟的又一个旅游新景区，坐落在市区以西35公里处。1986年，茅岩河在全国首创橡皮舟漂流旅游项目。茅岩河全长50多公里，两岸全是悬崖峭壁，河段多险滩、急流、瀑布、古木，有&quot;百里画廊&quot;之美誉。乘橡皮舟顺水而下，时而急，惊心动魄，时而缓，优哉游哉。一路赏夹岸奇山异峰，又可领略水上激情，二者可兼得，其中茅岩瀑布和温泉最为壮观和最具特色。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">推荐理由</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>是历史的河、在茅岩河的起点──温塘的议事坡下曾掘出汉代古墓，我们的先人在汉代时，就享受着茅岩河的恩赐，在这美丽的山水间勤劳耕作，繁衍生息。创造了一幕幕历史的文明。土家族英雄覃后为反抗元、明封建王朝的残酷剥削和压迫，率领土家儿女在此浴血奋战，留下了许多可歌可泣的故事和覃后王古堡，覃后洞，七年寨等许多供人凭吊的古迹。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;茅岩河流淌着历史，呤唱着历史。温塘至今古风依旧，土家吊脚楼鳞次栉比，古渡舰公依然斗笠蓑衣，呤唱着古老的船歌接送南来北往的客人。电影《边城》翠翠家的木楼，屋后的古渡摄拍于此。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>茅岩河是澧水的上游一段，这里有橡皮舟漂流的旅游项目，游人乘橡皮船顺水漂流，既可以欣赏美丽的峡谷风光，又可领略到急流险滩的惊险与刺激。茅岩河的漂流段在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>城西20公里青鱼潭往北的一段，这里虽然滩险流急，但河床坡度小，水位落差不大，险滩一般仅有20余米长，而且险滩与险滩间的距离又很长，所以在这里漂流是有惊无险的。　　&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>茅岩河的主要景点有茅岩滩、温塘温泉、麻阳古渡、茅岩河峡、水洞子瀑布等。河的两岸青山绿水，风光如画，故又称“百里画廊”。</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">市中心汽车站乘“市区-温塘”线路车前往<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>景区，建议自驾车。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">平湖游约2小时，漂流约3小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>平湖游与漂流，位于市区至桑植县的游览西线上，尚无旅游线路巴士，建议自驾车前往或在市区选择相关1日游。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">门票：A. 78元（平湖游）&nbsp;B.160元（漂流）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>桑植县<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1096.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">苦竹寨</a>（平湖游起点）/温塘镇热水坑（漂流起点）</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('22', '18', '娄江漂流', '14671025109152.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">娄江漂流</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">澧水河有两条最大的支流。一条是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>支流，一条是有着中国三大古道之称的排道支流－溇江！这里是湘西近现代史上最风云的一条河道。在当地还流传一句话“了解溇江，就了解湘西”之说！我们中国有三条最出名的古道，这三条古道在不同历史时期传承着中国的物质文明和精神文明！第一条古道：丝绸之路（由中原到西域）；第二条古道：茶马古道（由江苏、湘川、云贵到西藏或东南亚）；第三条古道：排道（由湘西<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1130.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">八大公山</a>、雪峰山、经溇江、入洞庭、出长江）。湘西石氏家族掌握湘西溇江排运的经济命运长达四百年的时间，传承15代18代扛把子。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界娄江漂流\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281019079733.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界娄江漂流\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">溇江漂流，地处张家市<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1198.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">江垭</a>镇，距核心景区武陵源仅30多公里（车程40分钟），交通便利。公司现有漂流船只120余条，可一次性接待1000人的大型团队，随到随漂，便于您的安排行程。随着上游水量调节坝的建成，游客将在娄江享受到更为惊险、刺激的漂流乐趣。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界娄江漂流\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281021115608.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界娄江漂流\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在土家族历史上，深受后人爱戴的土家族首领便是元末明初的向王天子向大坤，着名景区<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>便因向王天子在那儿率众起义而得名。今天，在我们溇江河，也有一处因向王天子而命名的景点：天子妃子洗衣滩。漂流的第一个险滩边据说曾是当年向王天子的妃子们为征战的英勇男儿捶洗衣服的地方。现在还有很多土家妇女、土家姑娘在这里洗衣服哩。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">历史传说</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">漂过一个险滩之后，河流的左岸是一堵石壁，呈弧形，上部延伸出来的地方有一根细长细长的藤蔓垂挂着，传说这是姜子牙当年<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1197.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">垂钓</a>的地方，我们叫它姜太公钓鱼台。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>来到这里以后，河道千回百转，但见两岸青山叠翠，山的走势蜿蜒曲折，抬头向上望去，四周的青山便形成了一个标准的圆形井沿，身在其中，坐井观天的感觉很强烈，真是山外有山，天外有天呀。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界娄江漂流\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281021266219.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界娄江漂流\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">这不仅是一段移动的风景，更是一段流动的历史，从东汉“娄中蛮”，到唐朝兴国寺，到宋代索口寨，到明朝<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1095.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九溪卫</a>，历史用大青石砌成厚厚的册页，在这里作着长久的陈列。“南北大侠”杜心五就从此地出山，从名重一时的“孙中山保镖”到技绝武林的“自然门大师”，都为悠悠娄江留下了一部永远无法复制的传奇。</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">建议自驾车。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">娄江漂流，时间约2小时，位于武陵源区至慈利县的游览东线上，尚无旅游线路巴士，建议自驾车前往或在市区选择相关1日游。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">门票：148元</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市慈利县<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1198.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">江垭</a>镇</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('23', '18', '五雷山', '14671025414927.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">道教圣地</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界五雷山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271124482715.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"449\" title=\"张家界五雷山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1073.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">五雷山</a>，原名雷岳，海拔一千米，主峰金顶分出数脉，呈辐射状伸延，有如淮南子天文训中的地维，因庙宇出现“雷扫其殿，钟鼓自鸣，尘埃自净”的奇迹，故更名为五雷山。山上气候宜人，环境优美，植被茂密，沟壑纵横，空气清新，自然景观独特，是有名的旅游避暑胜地。同时五雷山更是著名的道教圣地，素有“楚南第一胜境”之称。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界五雷山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271122545140.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界五雷山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">它与湖北武当山齐名，俗话说“北武当，南五雷”，二者如兄弟联袂，名闻遐迩，被尊为“中国南武当”。其道教殿宇之多被《三湘之最》誉为湖南最大的道教文化群落。据史书记载，五雷山道教“始于唐、盛于明”。相传西域净乐国太子曾选中此地，垒石室苦修，“得道高升”，这就是著名的真武帝君。嗣后，唐代李靖慕名上山草创道观。元末翰林国史编修张兑辞官不做，归隐五雷山，在五雷山扩修殿宇，弘扬道教文化，并亲题“楚南名山推第一”，从此五雷山名声大振，所建殿宇“旁魄百里，列县俱瞻”。 到了明代，常德荣定王、澧州华阳王对五雷山进行大规模扩修改建，建筑面积达5000余平方米，有36宫，72殿。其建筑为石墙铁瓦构筑，随山脊沟壑纵横陈列，绵延15华里，奇险深幽，玄妙超然，独具一格，蜚声南北。明神宗得知后，封五雷山为“洞天福地”，道教信徒遍及鄂西南、湘西北两省十八县。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">民俗风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界五雷山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271126172918.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界五雷山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">每年古历“三月三”（7天）、“八月十五”（15天）、“九月初九”为朝圣节，信徒昼夜朝拜，人山人海，锣鼓喧天，炮声如雷，热闹非凡，形成了<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1073.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">五雷山</a>盛大的传统庙会，有“朝不朝，一年十万八千到”的壮观景象。时至今日，三大传统庙会代代传承，年年举行。</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/271123428627.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界五雷仙山\" align=\"\" alt=\"张家界五雷仙山\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">五雷仙山神秘、神奇、神圣，古朴而幽深，空灵而厚重，它是大湘西东大门户一颗璀璨的明珠。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>慈利县建议自驾车前往；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">游览景区最少需<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">4</span>小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">可参照景区地图及标识牌，沿景区游道上山，欣赏沿途美景。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息：门票<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">68</span>元（单程游览观光车<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">15</span>元，不包含在门票中）。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('24', '18', '天泉山国家森林公园', '14671025686360.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">峰林峡谷</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">“湖南天泉山国家森林公园”即湖南<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>“永定区猪石头国有林场”。2009年12月4日被省政府批准为省级森林公园，2011年4月8日又被国家林业局批准为国家森林公园. 天泉山国家森林公园位于永定区西北部，东与罗水、桥头乡交界，南与温塘镇相连，西与青安坪乡相依，北与桑植县瑞塔埔白族乡接壤。属武陵山脉，海拔平均在800 米左右, 森林蓄积量15万立方米，森林覆盖率达87.4%，它的诞生对保护生物多样性，加快我市西线旅游建设和生态文明建设，促进当地经济发展都将产生不可估量的作用。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天泉山国家森林公园\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291039198166.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天泉山国家森林公园\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">湖南天泉山森林公园属武陵山脉，境内群峰竞秀，沟谷纵横，山坡陡峭，整个地形东西窄、南北长、中间低的狭长地形。天泉山主峰海拔为1264.1米，公园最低海拔为270米。一般海拔在800米左右。地貌类型为中山地貌。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300902531849.jpg\" alt=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界龙凤梯田\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;穿越<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1324.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">龙凤梯田</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：代天胜</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">园内风景资源独特，景观资源丰富、质量高，天然次生林覆盖率高，环境质量优越，气候宜人，历史文化底蕴深厚，民俗风味浓郁。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">优质资源</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">该园自然环境优美，动植物资源丰富，在湖南省森林公园中，特别是高海拔森林公园中，其丰富的动植物资源、众多的保护物种和稀有种属在湖南省境内首屈一指。该园地文景观十分奇特，特别是近20处各类岩石形成的景观，拟人状物，形态逼真。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300905105888.jpg\" alt=\"张家界天泉山国家森林公园\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天泉山国家森林公园\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">根据《中国森林公园风景资源质量等级评定》公园森林风景资源质量等级为一级。有<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>景区、七年寨景区、中山景区、祝融景区、覃垕王园林景区。公园瀑布、溪流多，空气负离子含量高，适合生态旅游。园内旅游资源丰富，旅游商品众多，开发条件良好。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">建议自驾。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">1.严禁在园区内野外用火。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">2.不要孤身前往，注意安全。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">3.园区内路窄弯多，进出车辆须谨慎驾驶。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>永定区猪石头国有林场</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('25', '18', '激流回旋', '14671025986760.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">激流回旋</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1076.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">激流回旋</a>漂流位于世界地质公园、世界自然遗产核心景区。武陵源门票站旁，高峡平湖一索溪湖下。重新包装后的激流回旋使整个游程增至1.5小时，集平湖游、参观奥运比赛训练基地、索溪自然漂流于一体，是世界水上<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">活动</a>的代表作，又是张家界国际旅游精品游览线，是您游张家界的必选。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界漂流\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271101533949.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界漂流\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">泛舟戏水、尽享自然一平湖游&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>潺潺的<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">金鞭溪</a>水顺流而下，与矿洞溪、楠竹溪、天子溪水汇入索溪。索溪湖两岸奇峰耸立，怪石林立，郁郁葱葱，形成了奇特的高峡平湖风光。漫步湖畔，扑面而来，湛蓝湛蓝的碧水瑶池，晶莹透亮;山在水里，水在山中，人在湖上，相映成趣;身在其中，水天一色，天人合一，如此和谐;怪不得江苏才女苏叶游览索溪风景以后，深情地留下这样的诗句：“相去千万里，心随月色归。来生甘作石，嫁与索溪水”。泛舟湖中，“小桥、流水、人家”尽收眼底，世界一流、国家二级保护动物一<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1133.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">娃娃鱼</a>及湖中小鱼，自由翱翔;进入湖里，看流泉，过飞瀑，踩花船，与土家阿妹对山歌;湖中戏水，打水仗，体验土家茅古斯泼水节。一步一景，趣味无穷，世俗凡尘的无限疲倦，在这群山环抱、碧水蓝天之间，荡涤的干干净净，无影无踪……<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界激流回旋漂流\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271102149855.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界激流回旋漂流\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">浪花飞溅、高潮不断一索溪自然漂流&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>放舟湖下，带给您的是另一番风景、另一种及至。激流险滩，浪花飞溅，飞舟而下，一路欢笑，一路尖叫，快乐无限;激流回旋，冠军瑶篮，激浪在奥运健儿的赛道上，徜徉在冠军的摇篮里，与浪共舞，乐在其中;自然漂流，有惊无险，在诗与画的于地间，在山与水的怀抱里，在粗犷的索溪号子下，让你充分享受激流与回旋带来的无限快感，奥运体验，高潮不断，带给您的是终生难忘的新奇体验。惊险、刺激、安全、方便，是您洗去旅途疲惫，放松、放飞心情的绝妙去处。1.5小时的游程，亲密相伴，使您的张家界之旅更加完美，余味无穷，不在遗憾，看山张家界，玩水激流回旋。<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">玩转激流</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;冠军摇篮一参观奥运比赛场地&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>2002年，<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1076.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">激流回旋</a>的创始人，国际激流、漂流协会主席西班牙拉蒙博士来到这里，优质的水源、良好的气候、适宜的水温、十分安全，令他兴奋不已，这位西班牙人抑制不住冲动，亲手按国际标准，设计了<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>激流回旋。建成后成为“世界一流、亚洲最佳”的世界比赛场地。2003年，这里成功举办了“五城会”和全国激流回旋比赛，继而成为2008年北京奥运健儿指定比赛基地。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界激流回旋漂流\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271102533524.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界激流回旋漂流\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">2004年，张家界激流回旋正式对外开放，陈至立等党和国家领导人来此观察，国家体育总局局长袁伟民参观后称赞道：“奥运健儿摇篮，时尚漂流胜地”。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">1.<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>中心汽车站：乘“张家界市区—武陵源”的线路巴士至终点站。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">2.武陵源汽车站：可乘坐<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1</span>和<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2</span>路至标志门的公交车至终点站，也可以步行到达。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">1.着装。衣服穿比较薄容易干的衣服或带一套备用衣，鞋子穿带鞋带的不易掉的。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">2.身上不要携带任何物品。漂流时身上钱包、手机、钥匙等物品都要放置岸上，不要随身携带。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">3.漂流过程中注意事项。穿好救生衣，系好安全绳，漂流过程中一旦发生落水不要惊慌，漂流水流一般不会很深，另外救生衣的浮力会保证你不会沉入水中，及时让队友把你拉上皮筏即可。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">4.关于夏日防晒。漂流季节一般都比较热，太阳会很毒辣，所以平时晒太阳比较少的你尽量涂上防晒霜， 这样可以避免被晒伤。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">门票：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">118</span>元。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('26', '19', '黄龙洞', '14671026247857.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">溶洞奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1079.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">黄龙洞</a>是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>武陵源风景名胜中著名的溶洞景点，因享有“世界溶洞奇观”“世界溶洞全能冠军”“中国最美旅游溶洞”等顶级荣誉而名震全球。现已探明洞底总面积10万平方米；洞体共分四层，洞中有洞、洞中有山、山中有洞、洞中有河。经中外地质专家考察认为：黄龙洞规模之大、内容之全、景色之美，包含了溶洞学的所有内容。黄龙洞以其庞大的立体结构洞穴空间、丰富的溶洞景观、水陆兼备的游览观光线路独步天下。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界黄龙洞\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261735206248.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界黄龙洞\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">世界自然遗产、世界地质公园、首批国家5a级旅游区张家界武陵源的组成部分。2005年被评选为“中国最美的旅游溶洞”。位于湖南省张家界市核心景区武陵源风景名胜区内，距离张家界市城区及张家界荷花机场、张家界火车站、张家界市中心汽车站36公里，距常张高速阳和出口20公里，有高等级公路张清公路连接张家界市城区和景区，省道s306直达景区，属典型的喀斯特岩溶地貌。1983年，黄龙洞由当地8个青年民兵发现。1984年10月1日正式向社会开放。自开放至今，已接待中外游客1000万人次。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界黄龙洞\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/241620135528.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"390\" title=\"张家界黄龙洞\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摄影者：向金次</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1079.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">黄龙洞</a>现已探明的洞底总面积10万平方米，全长7.5公里，垂直高度140米。洞体共分四层，整个洞内洞中有洞，洞中有河，石笋、石柱、石钟乳各种洞穴奇观琳琅满目，美不胜收。据专家考证，大约3.8亿年前，黄龙洞地区是一片汪洋大海，沉积了可溶性强的石灰岩和白云岩地层，经过漫长年代开始孕育洞穴，直到6500万年前地壳抬升，出现了干溶洞，然后经岩溶和水流作用，便形成了今日地下奇观。中国地质部70多位专家的考察结论则是：黄龙洞规模之多、内容之全、景色之美几乎包揽了《洞穴学》的全部内容，是世界溶洞的“全能冠军”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界黄龙洞\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261735588988.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界黄龙洞\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">黄龙洞石笋、石柱、石钟乳等各种洞穴奇观遍布，琳琅满目，美不胜收。水陆兼备的游览动线等，构成国内外颇有特色的游览洞穴。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界溶洞\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261736156312.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界溶洞\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">人类文化已进入崇尚王牌、追求极品的时代。被列入世界自然遗产的武陵源风景区，无疑是中华自然风光的一块王牌，而被国家旅游局列为全国35个王牌景点之一的黄龙洞，当之无愧成了这一王牌景区的核心。这颗深藏地下亿年的明珠，伴随着八十年代初<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>的对外开放而得以蛮声海内外。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">推荐理由</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1079.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">黄龙洞</a>以立体的洞穴结构，庞大的洞穴空间，宽阔的龙宫厅及数以万计的石笋，高大的洞穴瀑布，水陆兼备的游览线等优势构成了国内外颇有特色的游览洞穴，洞内有1库、2河、3潭、4瀑、13大厅、98廊，以及几十座山峰，上千个白玉池和近万根石笋。由石灰质溶液凝结而成的石钟乳、石笋、石柱、石花、石幔、石枝、石管、石珍珠、石珊瑚等遍布其中，无所不奇，无奇不有，仿佛一座神奇的地下“魔宫”。黄龙洞现已开放有龙舞厅、响水河、天仙瀑、天柱街、龙宫等6大游览区，主要景观有定海神针、万年雪松、龙王宝座、火箭升空、花果山、天仙瀑布、海螺吹天、双门迎宾、沧海桑田、黄土高坡等100多个。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">可在武陵源区乘</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">1</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">路公交车前往。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">游览景区最少需3小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1079.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">黄龙洞</a>外为生态广场，洞内为单一游览线，入口与出口不同，可以一路跟随景区导览员游玩。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">门票：100元</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市武陵源区索溪峪镇河口村</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '4');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('27', '19', '张家界大峡谷', '14671026491574.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 16px;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">峡谷奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">相传<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1080.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界大峡谷</a>原来有两个名字，一个叫做烂船峡，是因为从我们所处的位置上行一点五公里，就是神泉溪，整个大峡谷和南方红旗渠的水流都来源于这里。传说以前从泉眼中涌出过很多烂了的船板，当地人们又无法知晓烂船板从何而来，所以这里得名“烂船峡”。这个名字来源，有些地老天荒，海枯石烂的意蕴。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/261705127158.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界大峡谷\" align=\"\" alt=\"张家界大峡谷\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">另外一个名字叫做乱泉峡，是指峡谷中的两面石壁，溪泉众多，满峡飞流。这个名称来源，突出了我们<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>大峡谷风景区的特色，那就是峡谷中的飞瀑神泉比比皆是，一路游览下来，让人目不暇接。我们今天的游览行程是沿着面前的一线天绝壁拾级而下，然后顺着溪流的流向一路前行，一直到达神泉湖码头。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>，大峡谷就像是一位仙女，远离尘世，追求着天道的和谐与自身的完美。置身于此，薄雾飞天，天地只有一线宽，惊心动魄。观光滑道如仙女之彩带，飘落在大峡谷山间。玻璃桥，飞跃峡谷，惊险与刺激，大峡谷的自然神奇和谐天成。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界大峡谷湖泊\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261710026288.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界大峡谷湖泊\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 湖水</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1080.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界大峡谷</a>集山、水、洞、湖于一身，被誉为“张家界地貌的博物馆”！峡谷内栈道绵延数里，沿途飞瀑神泉比比皆是，溪水常年弥漫着一层薄雾，宛如世外桃源。其间植被繁茂，动物繁多，猴群欢跃，百鸟争鸣，鸳鸯戏水，令人目不暇接。</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界大峡谷\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261710556175.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界大峡谷\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">谷内独具特点的长约600米的诺克里娱乐滑道，可缓解游客旅途疲劳。世界最高、最长的玻璃桥——张家界大峡谷玻璃桥就在这里，还能一享极限蹦极的惊险刺激。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界大峡谷玻璃桥\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261706013033.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界大峡谷玻璃桥\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">主要景点有：一线天天梯栈道三叠游道平台吴王坡石壁裂张家界大峡谷缝全家福妇唱夫随千年古藤石上森林慈航普渡；天仙水瀑布曲径幽林闯王亭南方红张家界大峡谷旗渠天河观景台；翠潭揽瀑一路平安桥隔音石竹仙泉仙人洗面；蝴蝶泉瀑布怪谜洞佛手遮天烂船岩张家界大峡谷土匪洞等景点。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在武陵源区汽车站乘坐去往“大峡谷”的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">游览景区最少需4小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">乘线路巴士上山，从门票站景区进入，内为单一游览线，先从栈道下山，后漫步峡谷之中，最后乘游船出景区。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">门票：121元（含保险）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '2');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('28', '19', '老道湾', '14671026708754.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界老道湾\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261652216053.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界老道湾\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1082.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">老道湾</a>位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市城区以南，<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1127.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">七星山</a>北面的山谷，离市中心7公里，总面积9千余亩，因相传春秋战国时期，纵横术道人鬼谷子在此练功修行，收徒传道而得名。谷内绿树叠翠，山水交错，峡谷狭窄，森林覆盖率达到99%，珍稀树种<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1141.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">红豆杉</a>群落以及珍禽异兽在游道旁随处可见。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/261645038254.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界老道湾\" align=\"\" alt=\"张家界老道湾\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">老道湾一期试验型特色温馨树屋，共30多间房间，面积大小不一无一雷同，有单门别户，有阁楼小户型，更有楼中楼别墅大套间。适宜独行浪迹天涯者、年青二人情侣、夫妻、家庭团队多人等入住休闲度假。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">趣味体验</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界老道湾\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261646001684.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界老道湾\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1082.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">老道湾</a>景区分三道风景区，西线为仙女峡谷，七潭七瀑；中线为历史上繁华的千年古道，三十六绞，体现红色文化；东线景色为鬼谷峡，现已开发十八潭，体现鬼谷文化。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界滑索\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261647247588.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界滑索\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">滑索、滑道、水上乐园是来这里必须体验的旅游项目。想体验凌空飞渡，离开地面看看全新视角的<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>风光，可以尝试全国第一长的高山无动力滑索（全长800米，凌空高度超百米，最高速度超15米每秒）。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">景区尚未开通公交车，可以在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>中心汽车出站口对面乘坐至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1082.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">老道湾</a>直达车，票价5元。市区打车至老道湾平均一趟30-50元。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">滑索太过刺激建议小孩在大人的陪同下游玩，不建议老人游玩。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">票价<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">108</span>元，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1.3</span>米以下儿童，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">70</span>岁以上老人免票。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('29', '19', '龙王洞', '14671026959720.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 115px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">洞中精品，必定精彩</h3><p><iframe src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/360/754.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;padding: 0px;width: 720px;height: 465px\"></iframe></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">溶洞奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300858317903.jpg\" alt=\"张家界龙王洞溶洞\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界龙王洞溶洞\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1079.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">黄龙洞</a>、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1085.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">龙王洞</a>、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a>是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>三大溶洞。黄龙洞恢弘壮阔，九天洞原始野性，龙王洞最为神秘。龙王洞是在</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">1979</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">年当地采药山民从溶洞上方的“天窗”不慎掉进洞内，这个巨大的溶洞才为世人所知。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300853391507.jpg\" alt=\"张家界溶洞石钟乳\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界溶洞石钟乳\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">现已探知:此洞为特大石灰岩溶洞，年龄达3亿8000万年，全长33公里，现在已开发4.5公里，平均高度50米，宽80米，有58个厅台，28条石走廊，15处珍珠瀑布，3条地下阴河，湖泊2个，水花池45处，洞中石笋、石钟乳、石幔、石柱、石花遍布，琳琅满目。&quot;龙宫&quot;大厅有四根巨型钟乳石柱撑开一片洞天，喻为<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1085.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">龙王洞</a>的&quot;镇海宝柱&quot;，最大的一根周长达40米，高32米，堪称&quot;世界之最&quot;，已经申报吉尼斯世界记录，誉为&quot;天下第一柱&quot;之称，顶天立地、气势磅礴，令人叹为观止。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300858565998.jpg\" alt=\"张家界溶洞\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界溶洞\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">龙王洞属<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界旅游</a>核心景点之一，被溶洞专家称赞为&quot;世界溶洞奇葩&quot;，是中国最大、最古老的溶洞之一，具有极高的科研价值和旅游开发的价值。被学者誉为&quot;神秘、神奇、神得不可思议的地心之门&quot;。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp;</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站搭乘前往慈利或<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1198.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">江垭</a>的班车，在<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">306</span>省道<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1085.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">龙王洞</a>标示处下车，车费<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8</span>元。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">位于世界自然遗产武陵源风景区向东<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">30</span>公里与慈利县之间主干公路<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">58</span>公里南侧<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">10</span>米处，距<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市城区约<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">60</span>公里左右，省道<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">S306</span>经过景区，交通极为便利。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">门票：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">78</span>元</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '6');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('30', '19', '赵家垭朝阳地缝', '14671027229281.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">历史传说</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界赵家垭地缝\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281013272773.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界赵家垭地缝\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">赵家垭，相传因赵匡胤早年到过此地，与这里山水有过不解之缘而得名。与离县城28公里。暗河溶洞位于赵家垭水库底部，是一个外河流入型的水底大溶洞，洞高30—80m，宽道5—25m，全长1550m，洞穴廊道呈峡谷状态，走向由南向北穿山而过，落差80余米，形成于高山峰丛喀斯特峡谷流域，深切河床渗漏石灰岩断层层里裂隙，向含水层集中循环，再经溶蚀、侵蚀崩塌作用，形成与原河道平行的地下通道，是喀斯特区过境河的伏流河。暗河发育史应该与当地的喀斯特化过程同步，是研究当地峰丛喀斯特发育阶段和形成年代的重要走廊，过境河流在峰丛喀斯特及喀斯特形成与发育过程中的作用与意义，有待科学家作出深入研究。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界喀什特地貌\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281012352064.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界喀什特地貌\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界赵家垭朝天地缝\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/281012158967.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界赵家垭朝天地缝\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;赵家垭水库建成后，载流了这过境河的入口水源，从而把暗河运行轨迹形成的各类奇异岩溶地貌型态全都显露出来，有溶痕、流痕、波痕、窝穴、天锅、槽穴、暗竖井、洞顶穹窿、孔窗、岩底坎、岩边槽、岩角、磨坑、沉积砂砾石等无奇不有，洞壁沉积物有石莲、石须、石幔、石瀑布、石壁流等气势磅礴、洞穴水文景观有水池、水潭、溶泉、流水瀑、滴水瀑等，神秘莫测。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界风景图\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/281012471235.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界风景图\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">自驾路线：</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>火车站——永定路——常张高速公路——慈利县——三溶村——终点</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">1.开放时间<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">7:30-18</span>：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">00</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">2.注意出行安全，防止发生滑到、摔伤、碰伤等意外事故。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);text-indent: 0;white-space: normal\">3.走路要慢，把脚抬高一些，防绊倒。观景时，要停止脚步，看完后再往前走，切莫边看边走。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息：门票<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">111</span>元。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('31', '19', '苦竹河大峡谷', '14671027487424.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">峡谷奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界苦竹河大峡谷\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261655416293.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界苦竹河大峡谷\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">苦竹河两岸以岩溶地貌为主，又有砂崖峰林地貌，据地质部门考察，苦竹河、温塘、罗塔坪一带为北东构造，由青安坪 —杨家湾向斜构造组成。背斜核部出露寒武系娄关山群，向斜核部是三迭纪大治组，为海相碳酸岩建造，岩层主要有灰岩、白去岩、泥灰岩，两岸岩溶洞穴以千计。而罗塔坪乡驻马溪、双峰崖、寒溪沟等地，岩层为志留系泥盆纪石英砂岩，经长期的风雨剥蚀和溪水的深切，有<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>石英砂岩峰林景观。</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界苦竹河大峡谷\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261656000946.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界苦竹河大峡谷\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">乘船赏“百里画廊”苦竹河两岸风光，及游轮上土家阿哥阿妹的歌舞表演。沿途绝壁雄居、怪石重叠，有猴子捞月、血门沟、印花墙、凉衣篙等景点，土家英雄覃厚王的故事贯穿在整个游览途中。免费参观<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1096.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">苦竹寨</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1104.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">红军村</a>，苦竹寨建于唐宋，曾经是一个商业码头，非常繁荣。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img alt=\"张家界苦竹河大峡谷\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271550328254.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界苦竹河大峡谷\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;摄影者：郑亚平</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">千百年来，这里是一处神秘的禁地，岁月如尘，轻掩着一部古老的传说。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">迫近她，宛如闯进了隔世的梦培，纤尘不染的意境里，她会让你体会到什么是人间仙境，什么叫苍凉凝重。扑面而来的，不仅仅是风景……</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">建议自驾车；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">苦竹河大峡谷距<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市城区<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">5</span>公里，距<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1074.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅岩河</a>漂流下水码头<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">39</span>公里，距茅岩河漂流上岸码头<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">18</span>公里。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">建议安排一日游</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('32', '19', '九天洞', '14671027726740.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 16px;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">溶洞奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a>因洞内天生有九个自然天窗与外界相通而得名，享有“世界奇穴之冠”、“亚洲第一大洞”等桂冠。洞内总面积达250多万平方米，分上、中、下三层，最下层低于地表面400多米。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界九天洞景区\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271534253563.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界九天洞景区\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">九天洞内空气清新，冬暖夏凉。经初步探明洞内有40个大厅、3条落差悬殊的阴河、12条瀑布、5座自生桥、10余座洞中山，此外，还有不可胜数的五光十色的钟乳石群，堆珍叠玉、千姿百态。九天洞被誉为中国溶洞奇葩。在众多迷人的景观中尤以九星山、玉宫、水晶宫、九天玄女宫、寿星宫五大奇。九天洞有大、奇、美、幽四大特色，堪称四绝。&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">风光美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">1995年，被定为“国际溶洞协会探险基地”（全国仅二家），并被吸收为国际溶洞协会会员（全国仅三家）。经考察，发现洞内有古树化石和其它溶洞极少见的岩溶物质，不仅是难得的自然景观，而且有极高的科研价值。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界溶洞\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271534567257.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界溶洞\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp;洞内的36支洞交错相连，内有30余座大厅、10余座洞中山、6方千丘田、5座自生桥、3段阴河、3个天然湖、12瀑、3井等景。洞中石林密布，钟乳悬浮，石笋、石柱、石幔、石花、石人、石兽等千姿百态，五彩缤纷，琳琅满目。其中九星山玉柱、九天玄女宫和寿星宫三大奇观堪称景绝盖世，令人惊叹。</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">市中心汽车站乘“市区<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>桑植”线路车至桑植县城，再转“桑植县城<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>瑞塔铺”的班车至终点瑞塔铺，然后前行一百米到丁字路口，有前往<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a>的三轮车，一个人<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8</span>元；建议自驾车。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">游览景区最少需<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">3</span>小时。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a>，位于市区至桑植县的游览西线上，尚无旅游线路巴士，建议自驾车前往或在市区选择相关<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1</span>日游。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">相关信息</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">门票：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">75</span>元</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('33', '44', '土家风情园', '14671040857421.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">观风情园</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1086.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">土家风情园</a>座落在湖南张家界市城区，交通便利。占地80余亩,总投资近亿元,是以湘西人的土司城堡为基础，以最完整的土家山寨旧址原貌为风格，于1997年原址修复后向游客开放，是与张家界自然山水交相辉映的一颗璀璨的文化明珠，是土家人朝拜、祭祀、祈祷和节庆的“圣地”，这里保存着土家族千年奇风异俗，园中的土司城堡、九重天世袭堂、土家山寨汇集了整个大湘西土家人历史的精粹，是集土家族的农耕文化、兵战文化、土司文化、建筑文化、民俗风情为一体的民族文化景点,开园以来接待了以国务院前总理朱镕基为代表的30多位党和国家领导人，中央电视台、省级电视台多次对风情园进行报道，2003年被列入了国家AAAA级景区，现每年接待中外游客60多万人次，构成了“山上观风景、山下看风情”行程精品线路。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;<img alt=\"张家界土家风情园\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261103596630.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界土家风情园\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">土家风情园是原土司城所在地，土司城建于清庸正八年（公元1730年）。土家风情园占地达120余亩，建筑群主要有走马转角楼和吊脚楼民居群两部分。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"土家风情九重天吊脚楼\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261103415393.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"土家风情九重天吊脚楼\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">九重天吊脚楼为全木质结构，飞檐翘角，土家族民居里面的建筑元素在这里都可以找到，这里也是目前国内最大、最壮观的吊脚楼，有民间艺人设计建筑，高48米，九重十二层，层叠有致，从侧面看尤其壮丽。</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">民俗风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;民风民俗展示主要有土家婚俗、头饰服饰、蜡染、织锦、银匠、石匠以及奇石根雕，珍贵文物展等，还有整台原汁原味的土家文艺节目，如表现湖南土家原始劳作与生活情形的茅古斯舞、铜铃舞、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1121.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">摆手舞</a>、打溜子等表演。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"土家风情毛古斯\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261103105639.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"土家风情毛古斯\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">这里是集土家族农耕文化、兵战文化、土司历史、建筑艺术、工艺美术、表演艺术、民俗风情及饮食起居为一体的大型民族文化景点，有醉人的土家拦门酒，神秘的土家祭祖<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">活动</a>，土家历史文物展示，土家民俗表演，还有头饰服装、蜡染、织锦、银器、石器以及奇石根雕珍贵文物展等。拥有“九重天”、“千人茅古斯”两项世界吉尼斯之最纪录。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">推荐理由</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">园内建筑多为木石结构，雕梁画栋，金壁辉煌，飞檐翘角，玲珑雅致。代表作有土司城堡、摆手堂、湖南土家山寨、垕王宫等。特别是冲天楼，依山造阁，气势恢弘，楼高48米，九重十二层，曲径回复，独具匠心。</span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">到<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1086.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">土家风情园</a>，可以先坐火车到张家界火车站下，然后市内驱车5分钟到,即市南庄坪五子坡.车费不贵，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">公交</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">5</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">路、</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">10</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">路、</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">1</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">路可达。</span>包车去最多也不过20元。游客可以选择在离开张家界之前游玩土家风情园，既不用担心赶车或者飞机，又可以给自己在张家界的行程画上一个完美的句号！</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">票价：成人票120元，儿童1.2米以下免费，70岁以上老人持老年</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">证购老人票。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">开放时间：8:00-17:00</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('34', '44', '玉皇石窟', '14671041271630.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">历史文化</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;玉皇洞位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>城西约7公里的麻空山南壁，为清代本地乡绅李京开独资捐修。李京开又名叫李五瑞，别名九洞乐，号识破生。他生于乾隆七年（公元1742），道光乙酉年（1825年）去世，享年83岁。李先生家道殷实，富甲一方。少时勤奋读书，颇有才华，数十年奔波仕途，但屡试不第，官场无望，于是看破红尘，另寻安慰，请工匠，耗巨资，凭借麻空山天然溶洞，按上、中、下方位布局，巧妙构思，开凿成“天堂”、“人间”、“地府”三层共八个洞。另外，在离此约3公里的峰泉洞另凿一洞，故有“九乐洞”别名。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img alt=\"张家界玉皇石窟\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281156353643.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界玉皇石窟\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">玉皇洞石窟是一雕塑造像甚多，工艺亦较精美的清代艺术石窟。石窟上层“天堂”为雷电洞；“人间”居中，自东向西依次排列为玉金、毫笔、墨池、虎龙、狮子、孔圣六洞；下怪为因果洞，即所谓“地府”。从“天堂”到“人间”，自“人间”至“地府”，上下三层距离分别为60米和70米，其间由宽不盈尺的曲径于悬崖峭壁上相沟连，气势十分险峻。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">石窟奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img alt=\"张家界玉皇石窟\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/281156495858.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界玉皇石窟\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">玉皇洞8个石窟，反映的内容十分丰富，且各具特色，虽杂而不乱。它将石刻、雕塑、文学、书法等艺术溶铸于一炉，是古代劳动人民智慧的结晶。1959年，湖南省政府将玉皇洞正式列为重点文物保护单位。玉皇洞石窟风景区集观光、休闲与宗教<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">活动</a>于一体，景点内相应地开设了珍石文化区（天然石景陈列，考古石器、石雕艺术欣赏）、园林休闲区（画眉园、斗鸡场、重檐亭、水景、密林）、盆花、苗木观赏区，是永定区难得的历史人文景观，是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>精品旅游景点。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">从市区打车往<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1088.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">玉皇石窟</a>20元左右。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">乘坐公交车11路在枫香岗乡下。票价3元。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">该景点属于免费景点，该线路为具有一定危险的户外线路，游客切莫孤身前往建议聘请专业向导。</span></p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br/></span></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('35', '44', '溪布街', '14671041524772.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">溪布特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">“民族风情步行街”<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1089.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">溪布街</a>，依武陵源索溪河而建，是国内唯一集水上酒吧街、民族风情街、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1150.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">特色小吃</a>街等为一体的复合型旅游商业步行街，被誉为“不可复制的文化旅游藏品”。溪布，土家语叫做“<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1122.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">西兰卡普</a>”，原本是一种精美的土家族手工织锦，曾是土司王进献给皇室的贡品；而溪布街寓意为“布满小溪的街道，充满快乐的地方”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界溪步街夜景\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281151221415.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界溪步街夜景\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/>溪布街位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>武陵源区景区核心，武陵源区政府对面，北靠武陵源区第一大道——武陵大道，东邻张家界大剧院，西接前往<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1072.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">宝峰湖</a>要道——宝峰桥，南向沿400米索溪河岸布局，地理位置得天独厚，是通往武陵源所有重要景区的核心。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界溪步街\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281151500865.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界溪步街\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">名族风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1089.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">溪布街</a>由<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>金瑞旅游发展有限公司投资4亿余元人民币开发，项目占地面积约100亩，总建筑面积约7万平方米，项目建筑风格以湘西土风苗韵为基调，以传统土家民居为蓝本，依托索溪河自然水景元素，营造房中有院、院中有街、韵味十足的集市盛景，并融汇符合时代审美的时尚休闲元素，以“最原生态、最自然、最和谐”的开发理念进行规划建设，是全国唯一集水上酒吧街、中华名特小吃街、湘西民俗购物精品街、休闲客栈、创意工坊等为一体的大型的特色文化街区。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界溪步街\" src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/281152037513.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界溪步街\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">其整体规划以街巷与院落结合布局，力求浪漫、飘逸和通透，建筑风格融合土家族和苗族传统艺术语言，体现出古朴大气和原始自然的独特气质，是夜宿武陵源的游人不可不去的休闲之地。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">在武陵源区乘2、3路公交车前往。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1089.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">溪布街</a>交通十分方便，一般可步行到达，是武陵源区晚间休闲娱乐的最佳之地。</p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('36', '44', '天门寺', '14671041817305.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">寺庙奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天门山寺\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281140537775.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天门山寺\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>寺始建于明朝，历经儒、道、佛三教的融会变通，建寺以来就香火鼎盛，信士遍及辰、永、澧、常，是湘西地区的佛教中心，天门山也由此得名“湘西第一神山”。复建后的天门山寺占地两万余平方米，是目前湖南省境内海拔最高的佛教建筑群。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天门山寺\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281141199582.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天门山寺\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">寺庙坐落山窝，视野开阔，极目东南，庄严端丽，尽显天界佛国雄姿。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">天界佛国</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><img alt=\"天门山李娜小屋\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281145298984.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"天门山李娜小屋\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 李娜小屋</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">“承天地之灵气，接山水之精华，佛祖舍利给众生带来庇佑，也使天门奇景结无上佛缘。”<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>寺方丈怀梵法师引领着众人走进一个“天界佛国”，以最华丽的方式展现着湘西地区的佛教文化。1997年，李娜剃度受戒，法号释昌圣，从此遁迹空门。2009年有释迦摩尼故乡尼泊尔蓝毗尼迎请的释迦摩尼舍利正式安防在天门山寺，天门山寺成为湖南省内唯一一座拥有佛舍利的寺庙。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">在市区可乘</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">5</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">、</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">6</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">、</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">10</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">路等公交至市区<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>索道下站，乘缆车至天门山国家森林公园。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">该景点位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>国家森林内。乘索道终点下，山顶线路分东、西线，任走一条都会途经此地。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息：天门山门票258元（含往返索道、天门山寺门票）</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('37', '44', '紫霞观', '14671042137393.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; display: block; width: 110px; height: 110px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 110px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center;\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">历史文化</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界紫霞观\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281128155965.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界紫霞观\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1091.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">紫霞观</a>位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市武陵源区宝峰路，坐落在环境优美的景区中心，是武陵源风景名胜区内的主要人文景观与宗教文化旅游相结合的精品旅游景点，国家“AA”级旅游景区，张家界市道教协会会址所在地。藏有著名书法家的题词、碑刻及教祖讲经说法渡化图等宗教文物。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界紫霞观同心锁\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281128269236.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界紫霞观同心锁\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">紫霞观始建于明朝嘉靖年间，近500年的历史，在战乱时期收到不同程度的破坏。紫霞观是1992年因旅游事业的发展，教徒的信教，经政府的批准，由各地的善男信女共同捐资，当地政府拨款扩建起来的。道观共有大小殿庙30余座，计5殿、3宫、2亭、2庙、1阁、八仙山、仙人足迹石、中华同心锁等景点。中国著名书法家沈鹏先生为紫霞观题写了观名，观内有国内外著名书法家的题词、碑刻等宗教文物，以及老子教祖讲经说法渡化图一百余幅。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">建筑美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界紫霞观\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281128432861.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界紫霞观\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1091.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">紫霞观</a>观内巍峨的殿宇建筑群落金碧辉煌，雕梁画栋，布局严谨，供奉道教尊神。宗教建筑有老子出关亭、三清殿、慈航殿、祖师坛、关圣殿、玉皇殿等5殿、3宫、2亭、2庙、1阁，大小殿庙约30余座。现建有八仙山、仙人足迹石、南天门、中华同心锁等景点。景区内巍峨的建筑群落与亭林楼阁错落有致、环境幽美。终年香火鼎盛、朝拜者络绎不绝，因其确属一方不可多得的风水宝地，观内环境优美，交通便利，而享有“湘西第一观”的美誉。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">1、从武陵源汽车站搭乘1路公交车（1元/人）到天子街下，然后搭乘4路公交车到<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1091.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">紫霞观</a>大门下，打的5元左右；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2、从<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市汽车站搭乘至武陵源中巴车（10元/人）到武陵源汽车站下，接下来参照上面步骤进行，全程打的100元/车左右；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">3、从火车站广场搭乘公交车（1元/人）到张家界市汽车站下，接下来参照上面步骤2进行，全程打的（120元/车左右）。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">观内烧香属自费项目，不要听信他人花言巧语的游说。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">门票价格20元/人，对身高不足1.2米的儿童、残疾人和70周岁以上老年人凭有效证件实行免票；对身高1.2米以上的学生、现役军人、烈士直系家属、城乡低保户及60周岁至70周岁的老年人均凭有效证件实行优惠票。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '1');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('38', '44', '普光禅寺', '14671042405395.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">历史文化</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界普广禅寺白羊古刹\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281122490593.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界普广禅寺白羊古刹\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1092.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">普光禅寺</a>，又名白羊古刹，坐落于湖南<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>永定区城东，前有<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>，后又福德山（即今子午台），为一处古建筑群景观，现存普光寺、武庙与文昌祠等建筑，是佛教与道教的联合建筑体，融合了元、明、清三个朝代的建筑风格。寺庙建于明永乐十一年，比北京故宫（天安门）早七年，比湖北武当山金殿早四年，比四川峨眉山的仙峰寺与报国寺早建一百多年，历史悠久，名声远播，有“江南名刹”之称，具有很高的历史价值与观赏价值，被列为第五批湖南省重点文化保护单位。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">建筑美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img alt=\"张家界普光禅寺\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281123185474.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界普光禅寺\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1092.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">普光禅寺</a>整个建筑采用传统斗拱和藻井结构，设计精巧、宏伟壮观，由大山门、二山门、钟鼓楼、大雄宝殿、罗汉殿、观音殿、玉皇阁、高贞观、武庙、牌坊等组成一个庞大的古建筑群，具有宋、元、明、清各朝的建筑风格和特点，同时融佛教文化、道教文化、儒家文化于一体，普光禅寺是我国古代人民超凡智慧的结晶，在建筑和宗教方面都有较高的研究价值。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界普光禅寺\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281123294743.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界普光禅寺\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">普光禅寺整个普光寺形成了集寺、观、祠、坊、阁为一体和格局，这在国内实不多见。有人参观普光寺后即兴题写了一幅对联：“寺、观、阁、祠、坊一体，儒、释、道、文、武合流”。这十四个字是对普光禅寺个性特点的最好总结。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">乘<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">4</span>路、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">5</span>路、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">6</span>路、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">7</span>路可以直达；</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1092.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">普光禅寺</a>位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市区解放路（人民广场附近），在张家界市区的游客步行即可，也可坐出租车前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">游览时间在<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1</span>个小时左右。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息：门票<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">20</span>元。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('39', '45', '田家院子', '14671046831304.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">建筑奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界田家院子\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281210565474.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界田家院子\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">田家大院也称老院子，原名紫荆堂，始建于清雍正初年，是田氏族人的祖居，其建筑风格为四井封火墙式土家建筑，融土家园林、土家吊脚楼于一体，是典型的毕兹卡（土家族）民居。也是整个湘西乃至全国幸存下来，保存最为完好的土家古宅，堪称土家建筑的活化石，被誉为“土家第一宅”，他的外表看起来朴实无华，其实它神奇得很，可以说是藏而不露，深隐玄机。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"田家院子藏书阁\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281215345807.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"田家院子藏书阁\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">江南名联“世上几百年旧家，莫非积德；天下第一件好事，还是读书”在田家大院及其适用。晚晴的抗法保台将领土家军主帅刘明灯、民国总理熊希龄、曾任孙中山先生保镖的南北大侠杜心武、地质专家田奇隽、国务院前总理朱镕基等名人都曾在田家大院修习。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界田家院子\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281210098780.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界田家院子\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">学堂内有一幅朱镕基总理的手迹碑刻。众所周知，朱镕基总理书法功力深厚，但题字寥寥，仅在自己认为非常重要的场合才会挥毫。这幅字是他多年以后回到田家大院参观留下的一首七绝，十足珍贵。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/281209379688.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界老院子\" align=\"\" alt=\"张家界老院子\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">位于城区永定大道彭家巷，鹭鸶湾大桥东端，市内乘</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">、</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">、</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">7</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">、</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">9</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">路公交车直达田家大院（老院子）。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">票价：成人票120元，儿童1.2米以下免费，70岁以上老人持老年</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">证购老人票。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">开放时间：8:00-17:00</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('40', '45', '袁家寨子', '14671047085556.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; display: block; width: 110px; height: 110px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 110px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center;\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">古寨风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界袁家寨子\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281108070935.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界袁家寨子\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1093.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家寨子</a>位于<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>武陵源核心景区，是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1065.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">袁家界</a>风景区范围内的一个是私人建筑，当地地主的寨子，被保存下来，成为旅游一大景点。还保留土家族的建筑特色，屋檐角往外斜飞，屋檐下挂着一串串玉米跟辣椒，土家人民热情好客，喜欢用自家酿制的美酒招待贵客，喝酒前还必须唱歌祝酒。所以进门就看到一张摆满酒的小方桌，阿妹祝酒完毕，游客每人一杯。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界袁家寨子\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281108430984.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界袁家寨子\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/>&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">古寨特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"西兰卡普\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281109035579.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"西兰卡普\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">寨内有土家的三大特色之前就有耳闻“赶尸、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1116.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">哭嫁</a>、下蛊”，至今都是未解之谜。<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1122.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">西兰卡普</a>——土家族的一大特色， 是出嫁的女子用各色彩线一手一手编织而成的，工艺精美，费时很长。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界袁家寨子推磨\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281109255917.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界袁家寨子推磨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">1、从火车站乘坐<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>--武陵源班线汽车（时间约40分钟），到达武陵源汽车站，乘1路至门票站，购买公园门票后进入核心景区，可选择乘坐百龙电梯（需另付费）上山或经<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">金鞭溪</a>千里相会来爬山到达景区。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2、从飞机场搭乘4路公共汽车（时间约6分钟）到汽车站。乘坐张家界——武陵源班线汽车（时间约40分钟），到达武陵源汽车站，乘1路至门票站，购买公园门票后进入核心景区，可选择乘坐百龙电梯（需另付费）上山或经金鞭溪千里相会来爬山到达景区。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>唯一一处园中园景点，不设门票优惠政策，学生可享受半价，1.2米以下儿童免费参观。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">相关信息：门票85元。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '2');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('41', '45', '四十八寨', '14671047352248.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 16px;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">古寨风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291729008613.jpg\" alt=\"张家界四十八寨\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界四十八寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1094.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">四十八寨</a>景区位于慈利县广福桥镇境内，紧邻素有中国南武当之称的道教圣地—五雷仙山，总面积<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">44.43</span>平方公里。境内有<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">120</span>多座形态各异的奇秀山峰，传说闯王李自成在此建立联明抗清根据地时，依山就势建了<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">48</span>座雄伟山寨，并在山寨周围拦关设卡造<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">36</span>宫、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">72</span>殿，劈山移土建造近万亩军粮梯田。如今，还存有不少遗迹也没多少人知晓，俨然另一个世外桃源。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291729222513.jpg\" alt=\"张家界四十八寨\" width=\"730\" height=\"449\" title=\"张家界四十八寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">古寨特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291729463616.jpg\" alt=\"四十八寨李自成屯兵遗址\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"四十八寨李自成屯兵遗址\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1094.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">四十八寨</a>李自成屯兵遗址</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">境内“山、水、丘、平”兼备，龙形地貌举世罕见、森林资源异常丰富，自然风光美妙绝伦。风景区原始次生植物保存完好，森林覆盖率达到</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">90%</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">以上。野生动植物种类众多，达</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">1000</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">余种，其中被列入国家保护的珍稀动物植物达</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">80</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">余种，是养在深闺人未识的天然动植物园和中药材宝库。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">自驾车或坐车到慈利县，慈利东下高速后沿省道<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">S306</span>往常德方向前行，约<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1.5KM</span>后可以道路左侧看见<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1073.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">五雷山</a>山门，左转进山门，沿盘山公路前行约<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">22KM</span>到达五雷山二天门走慈济塔至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1094.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">四十八寨</a>。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">或可在慈利县城乘<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1</span>路公交车到达五雷山山门，然后乘旅游公交车到五雷山二天门下山后走慈济塔至四十八寨。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">游览线路可简要形容为慈利东下高速，自驾车或等慈利县1路公交车到达<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1073.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">五雷山</a>同门，自驾车或乘旅游公交车继续到五雷山二天门，下山走慈济塔至星德山赏<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1094.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">四十八寨</a>全貎。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">下星德山经双桥到老棚竹庄，看老棚古老造纸术，赏万亩竹海，之后经马栏峪、秤砣寨，登城门寨；从一天门沿三王峪到三元宫，观磉登群、秦角寨，在白衣阁吃中餐。下午经双云村进入李自成大顺军侦查营驻地探子寨，观五指峰奇观，登金龟寨探险；从双云村出发，探索珠宝湾，观高山飞瀑，赏仙人台、皇冠寨、雄狮寨等美景，考查唐代摩崖石刻，经过1、2号天生桥，到刘家大院吃中餐。下午经梅兴寨，看千年古松群，在太平村观景台赏四十八寨全景。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('42', '45', '九溪卫', '14671047594935.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; display: block; width: 110px; height: 110px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 110px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; text-align: center;\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">山城奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300847021165.jpg\" alt=\"张家界慈利九溪卫\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界慈利九溪卫\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1095.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">九溪卫</a>位于慈利县<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1198.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">江垭</a>镇境内，距慈利县城45km。东、西、南三面被娄水环绕，北面与紫驼峰相望。九溪地处武陵山余脉派生出来的北支。此支自青岩山入境，经茅花界北伸至鸡公垭分两支，一支东至羊角山分为两条，其中一条东延经赵家岗乡北部，江垭林场、象市、东岳观北部和杨柳浦北部抵石门县境。九溪城北为北山，海拔1105.1m，属中山(海拔&gt;800m)，九溪居娄水中游，海拔150m左右，相对高度10—30m，地貌属低岗地，由石灰岩构成。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">山城美景</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300847209213.jpg\" alt=\"张家界慈利九溪卫\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界慈利九溪卫\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">九溪古城森林覆盖率高，植被茂密，物种丰富，河水水质较好，空气清新宜人，总体生态环境优越，能满足城市人追求宁静、康体休闲的需求。九溪以深厚的文化底蕴为最大特色。城内人文景观星罗棋布，东街的兴国寺在唐代时声名在外，文昌阁也一直荫庇 九溪居民，使九溪人才辈出。另外，文庙、武庙、白衣庵、杨泗庙等也很出名。 另外，城内游道交织成网，方便游人观光休闲的同时，也成其为景观来增加九溪的整体吸引力。 明朝工部尚书有云：“三楚古来多福地，九溪应即是仙源”。高度评价了九溪的旅游资源。 总之，我们认为九溪环境优越，景观丰富，是一处观光、休闲、度假朝拜的好去处。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1095.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">九溪卫</a>在今<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>市慈利县北九十里。西南至永定卫二百八十里。建议自驾游。</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">九溪环境优越，景观丰富，是一处观光、休闲、度假朝拜的好去处。游览时间为一天。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('43', '45', '苦竹寨', '14671047821697.jpg', '<p>									</p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;display: block;width: 110px;height: 110px;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 110px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;text-align: center\"><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">建筑风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界苦竹寨\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281049509425.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界苦竹寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1096.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">苦竹寨</a>距<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a>5公里，为湘西北保存最为原始、完整的古镇，保留着典型的明代民居建筑群，具有良好的民俗开发基础。曾是澧水上游千帆林立的老码头、商人云集的古集市，梢公荡魂的逍遥窟、明清明代的万花筒。古老的风火墙、底矮的吊脚楼，向游人展示着土家人的聪明才智，一条条青石板、一声声咚咚喹，在诉说着古寨子过去的辉煌。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">民俗风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界苦竹寨\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281050224465.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界苦竹寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">苦竹赛是澧水边的一座少数民族杂居的村落，保留了明清时的建筑特色，民风淳朴，村民能歌善舞，许多<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1120.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">桑植民歌</a>都是靠<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1096.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">苦竹寨</a>的歌手流传的。入夜的时候，苦竹寨亮起了盏盏红灯，这是村里的一个传统。当年红军夜行军过苦竹寨的时候，村里有个老婆婆怕红军夜黑路难走，便在家门口悬起了一盏红灯，其它村民争相效仿，苦竹寨成了一个灯的世界。这段军民鱼水情被写成了歌，传唱到现在，这就是《门前挂盏灯》。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界苦竹寨\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281050327052.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界苦竹寨\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：郑亚平</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1096.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">苦竹寨</a>距离<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2.5</span>公里，市中心汽车站乘“市区<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>桑植”线路车至桑植县城，再转“桑植县城<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>瑞塔铺”的班车至终点瑞塔铺，然后前行一百米到丁字路口，有前往九天洞的三轮车，一个人<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8</span>元；建议自驾车。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1081.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">九天洞</a>，位于市区至桑植县的游览西线上，尚无旅游线路巴士，建议自驾车前往或在市区选择相关<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1</span>日游。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">相关信息：门票<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">98</span>元<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">/</span>人。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
