align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">民俗风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291400121137.jpg\" alt=\"张家界糊仓\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界糊仓\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">其中在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1097.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">王家坪</a>镇土家族聚居村落最为盛行的，是一年一度的“<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1123.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">糊仓</a>文化”。糊仓文化是一种区域性的农耕文化，最初属农事祭祀<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">活动</a>，经过长时间的继承和演变，成为土家人非常重视的年度喜事。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站有往返<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1097.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">王家坪</a>镇的班车，发车时间<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8:00-10:00</span>，每日两班，里程<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">60</span>余公里，车程<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2</span>小时，价格<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">15</span>元；建议自驾前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"></span>前往<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1097.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">王家坪</a>镇建议慎选农时，以芒种、夏至、秋收等节气为好，可以接触到土家人的田园劳作场景，寓劳于乐。盛夏之前的湘西山乡气候较为宜人<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">,</span>万物生长，一派生机，见欣欣向荣之感。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('45', '46', '贺龙故居', '14671117426919.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">建筑特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙故居\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281039427944.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"贺龙故居\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1099.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙故居</a>是一栋坐北朝南、四扇三间的普通木房，原是贺龙祖父贺良仕于清道光午间修建的，后为贺龙的父亲贺仕道所继承。贺龙和他的姐姐、妹妹、弟弟都出生在这里，并在这里度过了他们的童年和青少年时期。由于他们家人口多，贺龙父亲将这三间房用木板隔成六间。正中一间为堂屋，门首红底金字匾额上的“贺龙故居” 四个字为邓小平手书。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙故居\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281040078978.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"贺龙故居\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">民俗风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙故居\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281040362938.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"贺龙故居\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">堂屋前间过去是供奉家神和红白喜事用的厅堂，现在这里置放贺龙元帅身穿戎装的半身铜像。堂屋后面是退房，是贺龙姐姐和妹妹的卧室。左前间为火坑屋，冬天，全家人就在这间屋里生火取暖，来人来客，也都招呼在这里就坐。1916年春，贺龙联络20个人就在这火坑屋里商量过袭击芭茅溪盐税局的事。后面半间是贺龙父母亲的卧室。当地有个习俗，认为堂屋的左边为大(也叫东头，但它不是表示方位的)，应住长辈。客人来了，为表示尊敬，也请在这里就坐。堂屋右边前间是厨房，后面是贺龙和他弟弟贺文掌的卧室。凡卧室都陈列有木床、被褥、蚊帐、木箱、书桌、靠椅、灯盏架和女人做鞋用的竹篮、洗衣棒等各种常用器物。故居右边这栋房是骡马房，贺龙十多岁时为了谋生曾当过骡马客，在这里关养骡马。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">这是贺龙当年用过的马鞍、马鞭和斗笠。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">从<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>中心汽车站乘车至桑植汽车站（西站），然后步行至附近的北门汽车站，在高架桥下，桥下有一些停泊的巴士，乘坐往洪家关方向的车，终点即是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1100.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙纪念馆</a>和<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1099.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙故居</a>。返程的末班车在<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">18:00</span>发车。从桑植县返回张家界市区的班车最晚是<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">17:00-18:00.</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">此景点为免费景点，营业时间为淡季<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">9:00-16:00</span>，旺季<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8:00-17:00</span>。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('46', '46', '贺龙纪念馆', '14671117776366.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">红色经典</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙纪念馆\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281036505940.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"贺龙纪念馆\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">贺龙元帅一生忠诚革命，军中大将且高风亮节，一直受到国人的爱戴。贺龙是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>的骄傲，其故居位于桑植洪家关，目前得到较完整的恢复；故居斜对面，另建有<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1100.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙纪念馆</a>。前往桑植旅游，不可遗漏贺龙纪念馆。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">建筑奇观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙故居\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281037190635.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"贺龙故居\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;贺龙父母卧室</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">馆舍由八个展厅组成，陈列着两把菜刀闹革命、南昌起义、创建革命根据地、抗日战争、解放战争、国家体育事业奠基者、国家军队重要领导人、贺龙同志永远活在人民心中、中小学生思想教育展厅几大块内容。<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1099.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙故居</a>和纪念馆是全国爱国主义教育示范基地和革命传统教育基地。<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1100.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙纪念馆</a>展厅共辟贺龙同志及其任弼时、关向应等我军领导人的历史照片387张，文献文物190件。纪念馆于1993年3月筹建，1996年3月在纪念贺龙同志诞辰100周年时建成并对外开放，由时任中共中央总书记的江泽民同志题写馆名。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙故居\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281038206248.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"贺龙故居\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;贺龙家厨房</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">从<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>中心汽车站乘车至桑植汽车站（西站），然后步行至附近的北门汽车站，在高架桥下，桥下有一些停泊的巴士，乘坐往洪家关方向的车，终点即是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1100.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙纪念馆</a>和<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1099.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙故居</a>。返程的末班车在<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">18:00</span>发车。从桑植县返回张家界市区的班车最晚是<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">17:00-18:00.</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">此景点为免费景点，营业时间为淡季<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">9:00-16:00</span>，旺季<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8:00-17:00</span>。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('47', '46', '贺龙公园', '14671117968687.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">红色经典</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙公园\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/290831067632.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"449\" title=\"贺龙公园\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1101.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">贺龙公园</a>&nbsp;是为纪念贺龙元帅转战<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>而建，坐落湖南省<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市天子山上，在</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">1200</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">米的千层岩左侧，一般归类于石家檐游览线。公园内主要游览点有贺龙元帅铜像、兵器馆、贺龙元帅陈列馆、将军碑林（建设中）等。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">人文景观</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"贺龙公园\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/290831194788.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"贺龙公园\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">屹立在“云青岩”上的贺龙铜像与大自然连为一体，形成独特的艺术风格。建铸于1986年，高6.5米,重9吨,为我国近百年塑造的最大的一尊铜像。铜像背负青山，面壁神堂湾，凝重、庄严、和谐地统一在青山绿水的画图中，逼真再现了贺龙元帅的鲜明形象：浓眉大眼，八字胡须，右手小臂提起，握着烟斗，微笑注视着家乡石峰峭壁。身旁一匹好征的战马，昂起头颅，似乎在等待主人扬鞭踏上征途。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界天子山\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/290833276173.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界天子山\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">1995年3月28日，江泽民总书记为公园题写园名。胡耀邦同志亦曾为云青崖题字。公园内有数处观景台，是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>观景最集中的地方。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市中心汽车站（火车站旁<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">50</span>米）就可搭乘去往武陵源的线路巴士。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">武陵源吴家峪门票站进入：乘景区环保车至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>索道下站，乘缆车上山，或从卧龙岭步行上山。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">或者从<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1060.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">杨家界</a>索道、百龙天梯上山后，乘景区环保车前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">此景点在武陵源核心景区内<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1068.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天子山</a>景区，门票已经包含在武陵源核心景区门票内（<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">248</span>元<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">/</span>人）。铜像背后的不远处，便是“云青岩”观景台，从这里可以观赏到“西海石林”。西海是名副其实的山的海洋，上千座山峰风起云涌般展现在眼底，鳞次栉比，巍峨壮观。这里还可以根据不同的季节和天气而欣赏到天子山的“四大奇观”<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>石林、日出、云瀑、冬雪。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('48', '46', '芭茅溪盐局', '14671118381170.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">红色经典</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291530081822.jpg\" alt=\"芭茅溪盐局\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"芭茅溪盐局\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;贺龙元帅和<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1102.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">芭茅溪盐局</a>旧址</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">芭茅溪盐局是贺龙元帅两把菜刀闹革命的地方，是红色旅游景之一。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">1916年农历腊月二十八，青年贺龙响应蔡锷护国讨袁的号召，与12位穷苦兄弟首先拿搜刮民脂民膏的芭茅溪盐局开刀，一举端盐局后，回洪家关竖起了起义大旗。因为贺龙使用的武器是两把菜刀，从此“两把菜刀闹革命”成立贺龙元帅早期革命的代名词。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300833539925.jpg\" alt=\"芭茅溪盐局\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"芭茅溪盐局\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">盐局旧址，50年代初撤除1扇2间，尚存3扇4间原房陈设。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市桑植县芭茅溪乡。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">建议自驾车前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">此景点为免费景点。在去<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1130.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">八大公山</a>的必经之地。</span></p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br/></span></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('49', '46', '廖汉生故居', '14671118677778.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">红色经典</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291532111709.jpg\" alt=\"张家界廖汉生故居\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界廖汉生故居\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1103.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">廖汉生故居</a>位于桑植县樵子湾乡张家桥村三百墩组，始建于清光绪年间，为一间低矮的木房，小青瓦屋顶，六十年代，其弟廖章生修建了两间三柱四棋的木房，与廖汉生故居连为一体，1911年12月，廖汉生同志诞生在这里，并在这里度过了他的童年和青少年时期。廖汉生一九二九年参加湖南桑植苏区游击队。一九三三年加入党组织。土地革命战争时期，任乡苏维埃代表。湖北鹤峰第四游击大队副大队长，中国工农红军第三军政治部秘书，七师党委书记，九师政治委员，红二方面军政治部组织部部长，红二军团第四师、六师政治委员。参加了长征。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">历史文化</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291537044293.jpg\" alt=\"廖汉生\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"廖汉生\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 廖汉生左5</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">抗日战争时期，廖汉生任八路军一二○师三五八旅七一六团副团长、政治委员，独立第二旅副政治委员、代旅长，中共襄南地委书记兼分区政治委员，江汉军区副政委委员、政治委员。解放战争时期，任晋北野战军副政治委员，晋绥军区第一纵队政治委员，第一野战军一军政治委员。中华人民共和国成立后，任第一兵团军政治委员兼青海省军区政治委员和中共青海省委书记，西北军区政治部主任、副政治委员，国防部副部长，军事学院院长，北京军区政治委员，军事科学院政治委员，南京军区、沈阳军区第一政治委员。一九五五年被授予中将军衔。是第一、二、三届国防委员会委员，第一、三、四、五届全国人民代表大会代表，第六届全国人民代表大会常务委员会副委员长，党第七次全国代表大会代表，第八届候补中央委员，第十一、十二届中央委员。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市桑植县樵子湾乡张家桥村三百墩组。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">建议自驾前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">此景点为免费景点。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('50', '46', '茅垭红军村', '14671119152944.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">红色经典</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300830279080.jpg\" alt=\"张家界红色旅游\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界红色旅游\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1104.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅垭</a>，桑植县龙潭坪镇最偏远的一个行政小山村。全村分茅垭、苦竹溪、苦竹塔、文家界、谢家界，5个自然小组73户268人，生活在海拔1500米的<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1128.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">崇山</a>峻岭中。玉米、洋芋、红薯是村民的主要食粮。由于地处湘鄂交界，山势险要，易守难攻，大革命时期，这里曾是贺龙领导的红军主要<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">活动</a>地。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">历史文化</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/300831053297.jpg\" alt=\"张家界茅垭红军村\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界茅垭红军村\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;去往<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1104.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">茅垭</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1104.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">红军村</a>的路上</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">从1930年8月到1935年11月，在该村苦竹塔组，红军成立四届茅垭乡苏维埃政府，村民杨云阶、文昌和、文昌杰、李宏才先后担任主席，陈卜然、陶春轩、刘远茂、龚伦常、石长生、田和尚、唐世文担任副主席。从此，红色的革命烈火在这块土地上越烧越旺，在这里，红军和群众亲如一家，患难共存，同抵外敌，谱写了一曲曲悲壮的英雄史歌，茅垭成为名副其实的红军村庄。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">热情、纯朴、好客的茅垭人把红军部队当成自己的部队，把红军视为自己的亲人。茅垭人把最好的房间腾出来让红军住，留着最好的东西做给红军吃，红军和茅垭贫苦百姓成为一家人。苦竹溪住有杨曹两大家10多人，有杨青沛、杨青霸、张春生他们都参加了红军，杨青沛懂医术为红军伤病员治伤看病。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">地址：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市桑植县龙潭坪镇。建议自驾前往。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">此景点为免费景点。</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('51', '46', '金鞭溪红军路', '14671119403035.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">红色经典</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291157428511.jpg\" alt=\"张家界金鞭溪红军路\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界金鞭溪红军路\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1051.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界国家森林公园</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1069.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">金鞭溪</a>游览线上有一处路段被景区命名为<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1105.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">红军路</a>，很多游客走到此处疑惑不解，为何把这里立牌称为红军路，其实是因为在解放前夕，贺龙元帅曾经带领红二、六军从此地走过，为了纪念革命者的足迹，建立<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>红色旅游纪念地而设立了这段“红军路”。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">红色故事</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://manage.zjji.com/uploads/201506/291156387759.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界金鞭溪红军路\" align=\"\" alt=\"张家界金鞭溪红军路\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 