 rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>地区历史悠久的农耕文化、巫傩文化、建筑文化、服饰文化、饮食文化、婚俗文化，其中<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1120.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">桑植民歌</a>、茅古斯舞蹈、土家织锦、打溜子、<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1116.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">哭嫁</a>等更是列入了国家非物质文化遗产名录。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"烟雨张家界\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271938489921.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"烟雨张家界\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">这台节目是中国首台3D视觉大型民俗文化演出，也是中国首个模拟实景剧场演出，利用现代声、光、电等科技设施，配合美妙而震撼的配乐以及逼真的超大视频特效，真人与视频的完美结合，演员在屏幕间来回穿梭，让人产生亦真亦幻、如烟似雨的感觉，向世人演绎魅力、神秘的张家界民族风情。整台大戏时长只有80分钟，穿越的却是张家界几千年的辉煌灿烂文化。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"烟雨张家界\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271939090230.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"烟雨张家界\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"></strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">交通</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">自驾线路<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">:</span>长沙至<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>高速公路在阳和收费站下高速，到<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1079.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">黄龙洞</a>只有<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">17</span>公里。<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span>公交线路<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">:</span>张家界火车站距黄龙洞<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">48</span>公里有直达武陵源的大巴，或者从火车站打的至张家界汽车站再转车到武陵源。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">联系方式</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">电话：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">400-883-1111</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;0744-5628756</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">观演须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"></strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">票价</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">挂牌价<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">198</span>元</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">演出详情</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">时间：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">11:00</span>、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">17:00</span>，每场<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">35</span>分钟</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">地点：哈利路亚音乐厅</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('54', '48', '天门狐仙', '14671125256357.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">剧情介绍</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"室外演出天门狐仙\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271945442698.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"室外演出天门狐仙\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：李钢</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">《<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1108.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门狐仙</a>》是全世界首部以高山峡谷为背景和舞台的实景音乐剧演绎的是包括<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>内的大湘西流传的神话爱情故事。纵深5公里、海拔高差1100米的峡谷舞台，纳入了大自然的雄奇俊美。最高处是豁然悬廊的天门洞，山坡上建造了土家吊脚楼、飞瀑流泉、溜索、飞桥。这部音乐剧完全突破了人们熟知的舞台效果，融入了歌舞、武术、魔术、杂技等舞台艺术，宏大的灯光效果，营建出一个如梦如幻的世界。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">演出特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"天门狐仙\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271946402946.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"天门狐仙\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">《<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1108.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门狐仙</a>》又名《新刘海砍樵》。《刘海砍樵》是湖南著名的花鼓戏，主要流传在湘西一带。这出花鼓戏源起于神话传说，发源地在常德，讲述了樵夫刘海和千年狐狸精胡秀英的爱情故事。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"天门狐仙刘海哥\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271947011280.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"天门狐仙刘海哥\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 刘海哥 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：李东群</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">本剧通过对这个经典故事的重新构思、巧妙编排，并在音乐旋律的引领下，层层展开一幅幅绚丽优美、哀婉生动的舞台场景，重新讲述了以砍柴为生的青年樵夫刘海和在<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>中修炼千年的白狐仙之间曲折而浪漫的爱情经历。融入了桑植等地的民歌和土家的民风、民俗，在大型的真实场景中，表演的歌舞剧。以灯光和背景的大型营造以及歌曲独特风格为胜。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"狐仙\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271948171555.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"449\" title=\"狐仙\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;狐仙 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：李东群</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">地点：<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>峡谷大剧场</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">联系方式</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">电话：<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">0744-8369999</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-fami