INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('55', '48', '魅力湘西', '14671125484306.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">剧情介绍</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"魅力湘西追爱\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261117217884.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"魅力湘西追爱\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1107.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">魅力湘西</a>剧场的舞台演出持续了十余年，在国内、港澳台、日韩、东南亚均拥有极高的知名度，为武陵源核心景区享誉盛名的大剧院。</span><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">2012年龙年春晚的杂技歌舞节目《追爱》，便是出自魅力湘西剧场的作品。《追爱》原名叫《爬楼》，是魅力湘西剧场经久不衰的经典剧目。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;line-height: 1.5\">&nbsp;</span><img alt=\"春晚节目追爱\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261117590242.jpg\" width=\"729\" height=\"450\" title=\"春晚节目追爱\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">而在魅力湘西剧场原址，《爬楼》的效果完全超越春晚舞台的表演。灯光亮出，少数民族的阿哥从观众席中突然跑出来，通过借力用力的配合，身手不凡的演员们，瞬间窜上数米高的阁楼，展现演员们极佳的弹跳力和柔韧性。舞台上的演员们更表现出极好的平衡，能几个人同时在一张双脚落地的梯子上作出惊险的动作，引得观众惊呼连连。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">演出特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"魅力湘西\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261119006345.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"魅力湘西\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1107.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">魅力湘西</a>的节目取材，全都来自于湘西的民间艺术和生活：《边城》中的翠翠，划着小船出场，动如雷震的苗鼓，敲出了大山的力量。人们熟悉的<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1120.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">桑植民歌</a>《郎在高山打一望》、《马桑树儿搭灯台》在舞台上有了全新的演绎；<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1116.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">哭嫁</a>也被搬上了舞台，让人们欣赏到濒临失传的《哭嫁歌》。原始的祭祀舞茅古斯，延续着湘西人原始的信仰；神秘可怖的湘西赶尸，转成了一个令人感伤落泪的故事。湘西侗寨的《合拢宴》，在节目尾声将气氛推向高潮，强烈的节奏感，牵动着每个观众的神经。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"魅力湘西\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/261119359094.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"魅力湘西\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">室内演出之后，室外还有一场原生态的表演。苗族芦笙，侗族大歌，上刀山下火海，鬼谷神功轮番上阵，还有令人捧腹的互动游戏。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">市中心汽车站乘“市区<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>武陵源”专线车直达</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><strong style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">联系方式</strong></p><p style=\