 target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1113.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">荷堂艺术馆</a>位于张家界市荷花村，展馆面积<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">1200</span>多平方米，可同时举办不同类型、不同题材的展览，文化艺术讲座和论坛。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img alt=\"张家界荷塘艺术馆\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291954059116.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界荷塘艺术馆\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">历史文化</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style