 href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">天门山</a>麓，前临澧水河畔，四周为万顷荷塘。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">乘车路线：张家界汽车站（火车站附近）乘坐后坪中巴车，荷堂艺术馆下。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">游览时间大约为<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2</span>小时&nbsp;。【免费开放】， 周二至周日&nbsp;： 09:00~18:00&nbsp;&nbsp;； 周一闭馆&nbsp;&nbsp;； 节假日正常开放。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
