-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201507/011611347291.jpg\" alt=\"湘西土家织锦\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"湘西土家织锦\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">近年来，随着<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界旅游</a>从观光游向休闲文化游的转型，人们对民俗文化资源在旅游业中重要性的认识进一步加强，开发民俗文化资源已成为丰富旅游<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">活动</a>，提高旅游产品文化品位的重要措施。为了更好地挖掘、保护、传承张家界民俗传统文化，依托旅游发展民俗文化产业，2013年“<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1111.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">国聪</a>旅游民族<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1111.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">文化艺术馆</a>”应运而生。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">文化特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201507/011612063542.jpg\" alt=\"木雕\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"木雕\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1111.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">国聪</a>旅游民族<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1111.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">文化艺术馆</a>以弘扬大湘西土家文化为宗旨，是一家以湘西土家文化，民间艺术收藏，木雕石雕工艺，园林景观艺术，旅游文化艺术，农副产品开发，等收藏，展示，研究，交流，宣传土家历史文化，兼具古建筑设计、施工，民修古建筑装饰材料销售，古典红木家具销售的民间民俗文化艺术馆。它将成为传承保护大湘西历史文化以及发展文化旅游事业的先驱。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><img src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/301715302065.jpg\" alt=\"红木家具\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"红木家具\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;border: 0px;vertical-align: middle\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">交通路线</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\">湖南省<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;outline: none;cursor: pointer;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border-bottom-style: solid\">张家界</a>市永定区阳光酒店（张家界永定区永定大道2号）对面，出租车或2、7路公交车即到。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102)\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px;padding: 0px;font-size: 18px;width: 690px;font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;line-height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235);border-bottom-style: dashed;color: rgb(3, 159, 235);text-indent: 10px\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 30px;font-family: arial;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);white-space: normal\">游览时间大约为<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2</span>小时</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('58', '49', '军声画院', '14671126692275.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">艺术精粹</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"李军声沙石画\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291129194349.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"李军声沙石画\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1110.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">军声画院</a>的砂石画，是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>一大特色艺术。在近一千多平方米的展厅里，一幅幅用张家界特有的天然彩色砂石、植物所绘制而成的“军声砂石画”，为世人展示出灵山秀水和民土人情。透过这扇艺术之窗，您不仅仅可以看到一个更美的张家界，体会到土家人的聪明才智，更可带另一个“张家界”回家作为永久的珍藏。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"李军声沙石画\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291129367997.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"李军声沙石画\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">国家3A级旅游区，被外界称为“砂石画艺术宫殿”，位于张家界市区,距离武陵源风景名胜区约35公里，由现任院长、画家李军声于2001年创建，是展示新型绘画种类——砂石画的专题展馆。画家李军声凭籍扎实的美术功底，对绘画艺术进行了一次深入的回归性探索，以砂石、植物等自然材料为绘画创作原材料，创造了一种全新的绘画种类——砂石画。砂石画具有中国画的神韵，水彩画的清新，油画的凝重，工艺画的精巧，又有半浮雕的立体感，因其取材于自然而享有“绿色画种”和“环保画种”的美誉。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">艺术特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"李军声沙石画\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291130035431.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"李军声沙石画\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1110.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">军声画院</a>本着“纯朴、自然、创新”的文化理念，将艺术与市场相结合，将文化与旅游相结合，走出了一条宽阔的路，不仅为<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界旅游</a>做出了一定的贡献，而且在艺术界倍受好评。画院凭着良好的信誉和品质，独特的艺术思想和灵魂，赢得了硕果累累，相继被列为“湖南省57家民族工艺定点生产单位”、“湖南省民营企业500强” 及“湖南省首批文化产业示范基地”。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">游览须知</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">馆内3000平方米的三层展厅内，陈列着一件件突破传统绘画手法的以砂石画为主的系列艺术作品，让人视觉受到冲击，极具艺术价值与收藏价值。游览时间2小时</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('59', '50', '拜观音', '14671127193393.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">民俗风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281749592886.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1124.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">拜观音</a>菩萨是<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">张家界</a>民俗之一。俗传观音菩萨农历二月十九日出生、九月十九日出家、六月十九日得道。民间和佛门在这三个日子都要举行纪念、享祀<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/active/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">活动</a>。观音又叫观自在、观世自在、观世音，俗称观音菩萨、观音大士。观音为阿弥陀佛左胁侍，西方三圣之一，又是汉化佛教四大菩萨之一，汉族民间奉其为大慈大悲观世音菩萨。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">民俗特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"拜观音\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281750149837.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"拜观音\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：郑亚平</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">当地人每年都有在观世音菩萨生日这天上<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1090.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天门寺</a><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1124.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">拜观音</a>的习惯。据说拜观音前需净身、沐浴、食素三天。可以供花、供水果，绝不能供酒和肉食。每年的观音菩萨诞辰日，<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1071.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">天门山</a>朝拜的人从四面八方到来，可谓人山人海。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/281751132270.jpg\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：郑亚平</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;“庙里不断香，灶里不熄火，路上不断人”这是1949年前香客们到天门山寺拜佛朝圣盛况的写实。直到今天，许多人仍虔诚地相信天门山的佛最灵验。</span></p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `jingdiandetail` VALUES ('60', '50', '桑植民歌', '14671128144067.jpg', '<p>									</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">民俗风情</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"宋祖英演唱桑植民歌\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291110303708.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"宋祖英演唱桑植民歌\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;歌唱家宋祖英在维也纳金色大厅演唱<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1120.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">桑植民歌</a>马桑树儿搭灯台</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">桑植民歌是湖南民族文化中的枝奇葩，源远流长，浩如烟海，其特点是淳朴、真挚的情感而扣人心弦，曲调丰富多变，旋律优美动听。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">民俗特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"谭盾推介桑植民歌\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291112075691.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"谭盾推介桑植民歌\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\">世界级音乐家谭盾一直推介湘西民族音乐</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">桑植是个以土家族、白族、苗族为主体的少数民族县份。这些民族只有语言，没有文字，所创造的文化，多以口头代代相传，<a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1120.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">桑植民歌</a>就是他们创作的口头文学与音乐的结合。2006年被列入第一批国家级非物质文化遗产名录。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"歌手刘赛演唱桑植民歌\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/291113230643.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"歌手刘赛演唱桑植民歌\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;歌手刘赛桑植人多次演唱桑植民歌</p><p>\r\n								</p>', '0');
