-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/panorama/detail/1119.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"keywords\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; outline: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom-style: solid;\">花灯</a>，又名灯笼。灯笼是起源于中国的一种汉族传统民俗工艺品，在古代，其主要作用是照明，由纸或者绢作为灯笼的外皮，骨架通常使用竹或木条制作，中间放上蜡烛或者灯泡，成为照明工具。受汉族文化影响，在亚洲华人地区，许多国家的庙宇中，灯笼也是相当常见的物品。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.5;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界元宵节花灯\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271706123919.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"450\" title=\"张家界元宵节花灯\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;摄影者：郑亚平</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">花灯是中国传统农业时代的文化产物，兼具生活功能与艺术特色。花灯是汉民族数千年来重要的娱乐文化，它酬神娱人，既有&quot;傩戏&quot;酬神的功能，又有娱人娱乐的价值，现代社会多于春节、元宵等节日悬挂，为佳节喜日增光添彩，祈求平安。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; width: 690px; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 40px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(3, 159, 235); border-bottom-style: dashed; color: rgb(3, 159, 235); text-indent: 10px;\">民俗特色</h3><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><img alt=\"张家界元宵节花灯\" src=\"http://www.travelzjj.com/uploads/201506/271706581251.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"449\" title=\"张家界元宵节花灯\" align=\"\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(10